ad-tripping%20with%20babies%20and%20toddlers%2C%20Taylor%20said%20there's%20already%20more%20to%20pack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20already%20have%20equipment%20you%20have%20to%20travel%20with%20%E2%80%94%20car%20seats%2C%20booster%20seats%2C%20a%20diaper%20bag%2C%20and%20a%20pack-and-play%20popup%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBringing%20so%20many%20toys%20just%20doesn't%20help%20anybody.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20leaving%20toys%20at%20home%20has%20made%20Taylor's%20kids%20more%20content%20with%20simply%20looking%20out%20the%20window%20on%20long%20car%20rides.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20definitely%20learned%20over%20the%20years%20how%20much%20less%20stress%20it%20is%20when%20you're%20not%20worried%20about%20either%20forgetting%20something%20at%20home%20or%20having%20a%20filthy%20vehicle%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBut%20not%20bringing%20a%20pillow%20for%20each%20passenger%20was%20a%20mistake%20...%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224608%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Large%20pillows%20of%20various%20colors%20on%20a%20yellow%20chair%20and%20a%20large%20wicker%20basket%20with%20a%20white%20blanket%20on%20a%20white%20wall%20background%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bcdbba5da406397bf5ea56%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223456%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAlways%20pack%20pillows%20on%20road%20trips.%3Cp%3EOlga%20Peshkova%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20absolutely%20worthwhile%20to%20sacrifice%20space%20to%20ensure%20that%20people%20are%20not%20tired%20and%20miserable%2C%26quot%3B%20Taylor%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20learned%20this%20early%20in%20his%20family%20travels%2C%20when%20they%20would%20leave%20their%20pillows%20at%20home%20to%20save%20space%20in%20the%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20if%20people%20aren't%20sleeping%20well%20on%20a%20road%20trip%2C%20everybody's%20cranky%2C%26quot%3B%20including%20the%20adults%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENowadays%2C%20Taylor's%20family%20always%20packs%20one%20pillow%20for%20each%20person%20so%20everyone%20is%20well%20rested.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20a%20lot%20of%20families%20doing%20a%20summer%20road%20trip%2C%20this%20is%20%3Cem%3Ethe%3C%2Fem%3E%20vacation%20that%20they%20get%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20making%20sure%20that%20people%20are%20not%20unpleasant%20is%20totally%20worth%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E...%20and%20so%20was%20only%20packing%20a%20few%20snacks.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223117%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shot%20of%20school%20lunchboxes%20with%20various%20healthy%20nutritious%20meals%20on%20stone%20background%2C%20Top%20view%2C%20flat%20lay%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bcdd835da406397bf5eb64%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222338%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPack%20snacks%20that%20aren't%20messy%2C%20like%20grapes.%3Cp%3Edashek%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKind%20of%20like%20how%20when%20you%20don't%20sleep%20because%20you%20don't%20have%20your%20own%20pillow%2C%20we%20all%20get%20hangry%20and%20it%20can%20really%20have%20a%20huge%20impact%2C%26quot%3B%20Taylor%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BAs%20much%20as%20adults%20like%20to%20pretend%20like%20they're%20in%20full%20control%20of%20their%20emotions%2C%20hungry%20adults%20are%20absolutely%20miserable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETaylor%20learned%20this%20tip%20when%20his%20family%20would%20hit%20the%20road%20without%20enough%20snacks%20in%20the%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20have%20too%20many%20snacks%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20seems%20really%20obvious%2C%20but%20one%20of%20the%20things%20that%20we%20have%20seen%20both%20with%20airplane%20travel%20and%20with%20road%20trip%20travel%20is%20that%20we%20all%20get%20hungry%20at%20different%20times.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2