20Dhillon%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20are%20singing%20and%20rapping%20in%20Punjabi%20over%20Western%20beats.%20And%20they're%20not%20just%20catering%20to%20a%20niche%20Indian%20audience%20%E2%80%94%20they're%20filling%20stadiums%20from%20Canada%20to%20Germany%20to%20Australia%20with%20thousands%20of%20fans%20and%20taking%20over%20late-%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DG0JDN_q6RBE%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Enight%20stages%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20while%20proudly%20busting%20out%20Bhangra%20moves.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt's%20a%20very%20different%20media%20landscape%20than%20the%20one%20Sean%20and%20people%20of%20his%20generation%20and%20ethnicity%2C%20like%20me%2C%20grew%20up%20in.%20As%20a%20Pakistani%20who%20moved%20to%20the%20US%20in%202002%2C%20right%20after%209%2F11%2C%20people%20of%20my%20background%20were%20not%20exactly%20celebrated%20in%20Hollywood.%20We%20were%20cast%20as%20exotic%20oddities%20in%20movie%20franchises%20like%20Indiana%20Jones%2C%20or%20as%20comedic%20fools%20like%20Apu%20in%20%26quot%3BThe%20Simpsons.%26quot%3B%20The%20West%20perceived%20South%20Asians%20as%20one-dimensional%20when%20in%20reality%2C%20we%20encompass%20a%20large%20geographic%20region%20that%20includes%20India%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20Bangladesh%2C%20Nepal%2C%20Bhutan%2C%20and%20Afghanistan.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20longest%20time%2C%20I%20used%20to%20say%20if%20you%20were%20from%20another%20planet%2C%20you%20wouldn't%20think%20there's%20any%20Indians%20walking%20around%20anywhere%2C%26quot%3B%20Sean%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20very%20hard%20to%20name%20even%20two%20or%20three%20South%20Asian%20artists%20in%20the%20mainstream%20music%20industry.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%2C%20this%20demographic%20has%20grown%20so%20much%20that%20it%20will%20be%20hard%20for%20the%20music%20industry%20to%20ignore.%20A%202023%20report%20from%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fluminatedata.com%2Freports%2Fyearend-music-industry-report%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ELuminate%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20shows%20that%20India%20alone%20saw%20the%20biggest%20year-over-year%20increase%20in%20total%20annual%20on-demand%20music%20streams%20of%20any%20nation%20last%20year.%20Its%202023%20total%20streams%20were%20up%20by%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cspan%3Enearly%20half%20a%20trillion%20plays%20(%2B463.7%20billion)%20from%202022.%20The%20US%2C%20by%20contrast%2C%20saw%20a%20year-over-year%20increase%20of%20just%20184%20billion.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jay%20Sean%20wears%20a%20black%20bomber%20jacket%20sitting%20net%20to%20Veyah%2C%20a%20female%20singer%20wearing%20a%20teal%2C%20black%20and%20yellow%20striped%20shirt%20and%20Converse.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c3be591aa2ac29ee325a0f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJay%20Sean%20and%203AM%20artist%20Veyah.%3Cp%3E3AM%20Entertainment%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20internet%20has%20helped%20serve%20as%20a%20great%20equalizer%20in%20helping%20music%20go%20global.%20When%20Sean%20began%20his%20career%2C%20the%20way%20to%20get%20discovered%20was%20by%20showcasing%20your%20talents%20to%20record%20labels.%20Now%2C%20talent%20all%20over%20the%20world%20is%20emerging%20through%20platforms%20like%20YouTube%20and%20TikTok.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BYou%20could%20be%20in%20the%20most%20remote%20village%20somewhere%2C%20and%20if%20you've%20got%20access%20to%20the%20internet%20and%20you've%20uploaded%20yourself%20singing%20%E2%80%94%20boom%2C%20you%20are%20out%20there%20for%20the%20whole%20world%20to%20discover%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20Sean%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20fact%2C%20one%20of%20today's%20hottest%20Indian%20artists%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fdiljitdosanjh%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EDiljit%20Dosanjh%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20first%20broke%20through%20in%202020%20when%20he%20entered%20Billboard's%20Social%2050%20chart%2C%20which%20ranks%20the%20most%20active%20artists%20on%20the%20world's%20leading%20social%20media%20platforms.%20It%20was%20his%2011th%20album%20that%20finally%20got%20him%20there.%20In%202023%2C%20he%20became%20the%20first%20Indian%20artist%20to%20perform%20at%20Coachella.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20the%20winds%20of%20change%20moving%20East%2C%20Jay%20Sean%20wants%20to%20find%20more%20South%20Asian%20artists%20and%20promote%20them.%20His%20record%20label%203AM%20Entertainment%20has%20partnered%20with%20Virgin%20Music%20Group%20and%20Range%20Media%20Partners%20to%20focus%20on%20artists%20from%20the%20South%20Asian%20diaspora%2C%20regardless%20of%20genre.%20You%20can%20see%20his%20eyes%20glow%20with%20excitement%20as%20he%20talks%20about%20the%20project.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BOur%20first%20signing%20is%20an%20absolutely%20phenomenal%20artist%20called%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DxuILunIEi48%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EVeyah%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20I%20saw%20her%20on%20TikTok%20singing%20from%20her%20kitchen%2C%20and%20I%20was%20like%2C%20'I%20don't%20know%20who%20you%20are%20or%20where%20you%20are%2C%20but%20you%20need%20to%20be%20in%20a%20music%20studio%2C%20not%20in%20a%20kitchen%20with%20a%20voice%20like%20that.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFinding%20new%20South%20Asian%20talent%20is%20part%20of%20Sean's%20effort%20to%20give%20back%20to%20his%20community.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BIt%20really%20was%20and%20has%20been%20important%20for%20the%20la