ion%20in%20the%20Hayes%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20probably%20has%20her%20name%20trademarked%2C%20just%20like%20Aretha%20Franklin%20and%20others%20I've%20represented%20own%20their%20trademarks%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20protect%20your%20brand%2C%20your%20trademark%2C%20and%20when%20you%20don't%20respond%20immediately%2C%20that's%20conveying%20that%20you're%20accepting%20this%2C%20and%20then%20others%20will%20do%20it.''%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESwift%20can%20claim%20trademark%20infringement%20by%20arguing%20that%20Trump's%20campaign%20gets%20an%20unauthorized%20benefit%20from%20reposting%20the%20bogus%20endorsement%2C%20added%20Paul%20Michael%20Wilson%2C%20a%20trademark%20expert%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwalkerandassoc.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWalker%20%26amp%3B%20Associates%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20really%20bad%20%E2%80%94%20somebody%20should%20have%20told%20him%20not%20to%20do%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Wilson%20said%20with%20a%20laugh.%20%26quot%3BLike%2C%20really%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWalker%2C%20Wilson%2C%20and%20others%20cited%20the%20Lanham%20Act%20of%201946%2C%20a%20federal%20statute%20that%20protects%20trademarked%20commercial%20interests%20against%20unauthorized%20use%2C%20false%20advertising%2C%20and%20unfair%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20could%20make%20a%20case%20that%20Trump's%20post%20is%20an%20advertisement%26quot%3B%20protected%20under%20the%20act%2C%20said%20Jessica%20Litman%2C%20who%20teaches%20trademark%20and%20copyright%20law%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Michigan.%20Still%2C%20Litman%20said%20she'd%20%26quot%3Bexpect%20a%20court%20to%20exercise%20caution%20to%20avoid%20chilling%20political%20speech.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2241d5edbc-b2fb-407b-a7f0-6c379ee09331%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Being%20clueless%20is%20not%20a%20defense'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20out%20of%20the%20question%20that%20he