rk%20Bartholomew%2C%20a%20law%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20at%20Buffalo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20would%20be%20the%20key%20place%20for%20Swift%20to%20look%2C%26quot%3B%20Bartholomew%20said.%20%26quot%3BIntent%20would%20be%20key.%20Swift%20would%20need%20to%20prove%20that%20the%20Trump%20campaign%20sent%20these%20images%20out%20with%20intent%20to%20deceive%20voters.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESwift%20is%20from%20Tennessee%2C%20and%20if%20she%20were%20to%20sue%20there%2C%20that%20state%20just%20passed%20the%20ELVIS%20Act%2C%20which%20lets%20people%20sue%20someone%20for%20using%20a%20deepfake%20of%20their%20likeness%20for%20fundraising%2C%20said%20Juan%20Perla%2C%20a%20partner%20at%20New%20York-headquartered%20international%20firm%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.curtis.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECurtis%2C%20Mallet-Prevost%2C%20Colt%20%26amp%3B%20Mosle%20LLP%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20suing%2C%20Swift%20may%20be%20entitled%20to%20a%20judge's%20injunction%20%E2%80%94%20at%20least%20temporarily%20%E2%80%94%20ordering%20Trump%20to%20take%20the%20post%20down%2C%20Perla%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20what%20is%20more%20likely%20to%20happen%20first%20is%20similar%20to%20what%20Celine%20Dion%20did%2C%20when%20she%20criticized%20and%20poked%20fun%20at%20the%20Trump-Vance%20campaign%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fceline-dion-rebukes-donald-trump-unauthorized-titanic-song-rally-rally2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efor%20using%20her%20Titanic%20theme%20song%20%3C%2Fa%3Eat%20one%20of%20their%20rallies%20without%20her%20permission%2C%26quot%3B%20Perla%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20worked%20for%20Johansson%2C%20at%20least.%20The%20OpenAI's%20new%20chatbot%20voices%20recently%20began%20to%20roll%20out%20to%20select%20users%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20voice%20resembling%20that%20of%20the%20actor%20is%20nowhere%20to%20be%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca