3Cli%3EThe%20four-day%20event%2C%20which%20will%20end%20on%20August%2022%2C%20will%20officially%20nominate%20Kamala%20Harris's%20Vice%20President%20pick%2C%20Minnesota%20Governor%20Tim%20Walz%2C%20in%20the%20presidential%20elections.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFormer%20US%20Presidents%20Barack%20Obama%20and%20Bill%20Clinton%20are%20expected%20to%20speak%20at%20the%20National%20Convention%20and%20bid%20adieu%20to%20Joe%20Biden.%20The%20Democrats%20will%20also%20honour%20Hilary%20Clinton%2C%20their%20official%20candidate%20who%20lost%20to%20Donald%20Trump%20in%20the%202016%20US%20Presidential%20Elections.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELast%20month%2C%20Mr%20Biden%20dropped%20out%20of%20the%20Presidential%20race%20just%20100%20days%20before%20the%20election%2C%20an%20unprecedented%20move%20in%20modern%20US%20political%20history.%20Concerns%20over%20the%2081-year-old's%20health%20surrounded%20the%20Presidential%20campaigns%2C%20with%20rival%20Republicans%20targeting%20the%20Democrats%20over%20the%20issue.%20The%20concerns%20were%20aggravated%20after%20Biden's%20presidential%20debate%20with%20Trump%20in%20June.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETo%20designate%20a%20formal%20nominee%2C%20delegates%20chosen%20from%2050%20US%20states%2C%20the%20US%20capital%20and%20overseas%20territories%20attend%20their%20party's%20nominating%20convention%20to%20officially%20anoint%20the%20candidate.%20Biden%20backed%20Kamala%20Harris%20as%20the%20candidate%20which%20was%20later%20endorsed%20by%20several%20leaders%20including%20former%20US%20President%20Barack%20Obama.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EJoe%20Biden%20will%20give%20a%20prime-time%20address%20and%20make%20a%20case%20for%20his%20incumbent%20deputy%2C%20Kamala%20Harris%2C%20who%20is%20up%20against%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20the%20former%20US%20President%2C%20with%20multiple%20court%20cases%20and%20survivor%20of%20an%20assassination%20attempt.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20the%20Primary%20Election%2C%20a%20poll%20where%20parties%20select%20their%20candidates%20for%20the%20general%20election%2C%20Joe%20Biden%20won%20overwhelmingly%20with%2087.1%20per%20cent%20votes.%20The%2026th%20Democratic%20National%20Convention%20will%20serve%20as%20a%20farewell%20for%20Mr%20Biden%20as%20he%20hangs%20up%20his%20boots.%20In%201968%2C%20President%20Lyndon%20B%20Johnson%20declared%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20Vietnam%20War%20that%20he%20would%20not%20run%20for%20re-election.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EKamala%20Harris%2C%20the%20first%20Black%20and%20South%20Asian%20US%20Vice%20President%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20share%20the%20stage%20with%20Mr%20Biden.%20Kamala%20Harris%2C%20who%20considers%20herself%20an%20%26quot%3Bunderdog%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20race%20against%20Trump%2C%20earlier%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20work%20has%20to%20be%20done%20to%20earn%20the%20vote%20of%20the%20American%20people%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESecurity%20has%20been%20increased%20near%20the%20convention%20centre%20in%20Chicago%20after%20an%20array%20of%20possible%20threats%2C%20including%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20protesters%20opposing%20Biden's%20support%20for%20Israel's%20actions%20in%20Gaza.%20They%20are%20expected%20to%20march%20through%20the%20city%20outside%20the%20security%20perimeter.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Secret%20Service%2C%20FBI%20and%20the%20local%20police%20reportedly%20spent%20a%20year%20formulating%20a%20security%20plan%20and%20cordoning%20off%20areas%20near%20the%20United%20Center%20Arena%20where%20the%20convention%20will%20take%20place.%20Musicians%20and%20Hollywood%20celebrities%20are%20expected%20to%20attend%20the%20event.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELast%20week%2C%20Biden%20and%20Harris%20had%20put%20up%20a%20show%20of%20unity%20in%20Maryland%20when%20they%20made%20their%20first%20joint%20trip%20since%20the%20change%20of%20the%20Democratic%20Party's%20plans%20for%20the%20Presidential%20Elections.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724103000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-10%2F90qr96k8_kamala-ha