-taxi-hacks-emmys-1236106140%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ftv%2Factors%2Fchristopher-lloyd-sitcoms-taxi-hacks-emmys-1236106140%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20new%20programming%20deal%20shows%20why%20Netflix%20has%20all%20the%20leverage%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221260%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Characters%20from%20%26quot%3BBreaking%20Bad%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c3b229b4912df3ae1cc526%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22709%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BBreaking%20Bad's%26quot%3B%20Walter%20White%2C%20Skyler%20White%2C%20and%20Walter%20White%20Jr.%2C%20are%20part%20of%20the%20AMC%20Collection%20on%20Netflix.%20Will%20anyone%20notice%20the%20%26quot%3BAMC%26quot%3B%20part%3F%3Cp%3EDoug%20Hyun%20%2F%20AMC%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ENetflix%20wants%20you%20to%20think%20of%20things%20you%20see%20on%20Netflix%20as%20Netflix%20shows%20and%20movies.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20people%20who%20license%20those%20movies%20and%20TV%20shows%20wish%20you%20thought%20of%20them%20as%20NBC%20shows%2C%20or%20Disney%20movies%2C%20or%20whatever.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20new%20deal%20with%20AMC%20Networks%20shows%20you%20how%20hard%20it%20is%20for%20the%20media%20companies%20to%20get%20what%20they%20want%20from%20Netflix.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThought%20experiment%3A%20Let's%20say%20you%20run%20a%20big%20TV%20network.*%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20let's%20say%20you%20decide%20to%20license%20some%20of%20your%20TV%20shows%20to%20Netflix.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20happens%20next%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20you%20get%20a%20bunch%20of%20money%2C%20at%20something%20close%20to%20100%25%20margin.%20You've%20already%20paid%20to%20make%20these%20shows%2C%20and%20(hopefully)%20made%20some%20money%20from%20them.%20Now%20Netflix%20is%20paying%20you%20again.%20Great!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20happens%20next%20is%20up%20for%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20possibility%20is%20that%20Netflix%20users%20watch%20your%20show%2C%20then%20realize%20that%20it%20came%20from%20your%20network%2C%20and%20then%20eventually%20make%20their%20way%20over%20to%20your%20network%20to%20watch%20more%20of%20your%20programming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20what%20happened%20years%20ago%20when%20Netflix%20started%20showing%20old%20episodes%20of%20AMC's%20%26quot%3BBreaking%20Bad%26quot%3B%20while%20AMC%20was%20still%20airing%20new%20episodes%20of%20the%20show%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vox.com%2Frecode%2F2020%2F7%2F14%2F21312595%2Fnetflix-breaking-bad-podcast-streaming-land-of-the-giants%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BBreaking%20Bad's%26quot%3B%20ratings%20shot%20up%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20is%20good%20for%20the%20long-term%20health%20of%20your%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20possibility%20is%20that%20Netflix%20users%20watch%20your%20show%2C%20have%20no%20idea%20it%20came%20from%20your%20network%2C%20and%20don't%20care.%20They%20just%20think%20it's%20a%20Netflix%20show%20because%20they%20saw%20it%20on%20Netflix.%20This%20is%20bad%20for%20the%20long-term%20health%20of%20your%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20that%20both%20possibilities%20exist%20helps%20explain%20why%20big%20media%20companies%20have%20taken%20an%20on-off-on%20approach%20to%20licensing%20their%20stuff%20to%20Netflix.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20when%20Netflix%20was%20just%20building%20its%20streaming%20business%2C%20big%20media%20was%20happy%20to%20do%20those%20deals%20and%20thought%20Netflix%20was%20kind%20of%20a%20sucker.%20Then%2C%20once%20they%20realized%20Netflix%20was%20killing%20them%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vox.com%2F2017%2F8%2F8%2F16115402%2Fdisney-netflix-espn-streaming-service-2018-2019%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethey%20pulled%20a%20lot%20of%20their%20stuff%20off%20of%20Netflix%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20put%20it%20onto%20their%20own%20streaming%20services.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vox.com%2Ftechnology%2F2023%2F6%2F21%2F23768778%2Fhbo-netflix-insecure-streaming-amazon-peter-kafka-media-column%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENow%20they've%20started%20selling%20Netflix%20their%20good%20stuff%2C%20again%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vox.com%2Ftechnology%2F2023%2F10%2F4%2F23903539%2Fdune-netflix-max-streaming-wbd-hbo-peter-kafka-newsletter%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebecause%20they%20need%20the%20money%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhich%20brings%20us%20to%20Monday%20%E2%80%94%20the%20first%20day%20of%20a%20new%20licensing%20deal%20between%20AMC%20and%20Netflix.%20In%20addition%20to%20licensing%20shows%20that%20have%20been%20on%20Netflix%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20like%20%26quot%3BBreaking%20Bad%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BThe%20Walking%20Dead%2C%26quot%3B%20AMC%20is%20now%20also%20selling%20the%20streaming%20rights%20to%20shows%20you%20may%20not%20have%20seen%20or%20even%20heard%20about%2C%20like%20%26quot%3BAnne%20Rice's%20Interview%20with%20the%20Vampire%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BMonsieur%20Spade.%26quot%3B%20That's%20all%20very%20standard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20appears%20to%20be%20new%20is%20that%20Netflix%20has%20now%20agreed%20to%20group%20all%20of%20AMC's%20shows%20together%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bcollection.%26quot%3B%20So%20that%2C%20in%20theory%2C%20a%20%26quot%3BBetter%20Call%20Saul%26quot%3B%20fan%20might%20learn%20that%20the%20show%20is%20from%20AMC%2C%20and%20that%20AMC%20also%20has%20%26quot%3BGangs%20of%20London.%26quot%3B%20And%20you%20can%20see%20the%20first%20two%20seasons%20of%20that%20on%20Netflix%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAMC%20is%20psyched%20about%20this%2C%20and%20called%20it%20out%20on%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finvestors.amcnetworks.com%2Fnews-releases%2Fnews-release-details%2Famc-networks-inc-reports-second-quarter-2024-results%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eearnings%20call%20earlier%20this%20summer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20describing%20it%20as%20%26quot%3Ban%20innovative%20deal%20to%20strategically%20curate%20and%20window%20prior%20seasons%20of%2015%20AMC%20branded%20shows%26quot%3B%20on%20Netflix.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20pay%20a%20lot%20of%20attention%20to%20Netflix%2C%20and%20I've%20never%20seen%20the%20streamer%20emphasize%20the%20network%20or%20studio%20something%20comes%20from.%20Unless%20it%20can%20call%20something%20a%20%26quot%3BNetflix%20Original%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20it%20does%20a%20lot%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.quora.com%2FWhy-does-Netflix-label-shows-it-purchased-Netflix-Originals-when-it-didnt-originate-from-Netflix%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThey%2520are%2520commissioned%2520by%2520Netflix%2Cthem%252C%2520Netflix%2520does%2520the%2520same.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esometimes%20even%20when%20that's%20a%20bit%20misleading%3C%2Fa%3E).%20And%20I%20know%20that's%20definitely%20something%20the%20TV%20and%20movie%20guys%20have%20asked%20for%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20I%20was%20curious%20to%20see%20what%20this%20looked%20like%2C%20and%20%E2%80%A6%20boy%20was%20it%20hard%20to%20find.%20There's%20nothing%20on%20my%20Netflix%20home%20screen%20%E2%80%94%20either%20on%20my%20phone%20or%20my%20TV%20%E2%80%94%20that%20indicates%20there's%20an%20AMC%20%26quot%3Bcollection%2C%26quot%3B%20even%20though%20Netflix%20knows%20I've%20watched%20a%20lot%20of%20AMC%20shows%20like%20%26quot%3BBreaking%20Bad%26quot%3B%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20I%20knew%20it's%20supposed%20to%20exist%2C%20I%20did%20type%20in%20%26quot%3BAMC%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20Netflix%20search%20bar%20and%20eventually%20got%20this%20page%2C%20which%20is%20indeed%20a%20curated%20collection%20of%20things%20made%20by%20AMC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Screenshot%20of%20%26quot%3BAMC%20Collection%26quot%3B%20on%20Netflix%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c3a0591aa2ac29ee324973%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222778%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ENetflix%20via%20screenshot%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20are%20the%20odds%20someone%20types%20%26quot%3BAMC%26quot%3B%20into%20a%20Netflix%20search%20bar%3F%20I'm%20guessing%20very%2C%20very%20low.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20to%20be%20more%20to%20this%2C%20right%3F%20Surely%20Netflix%20will%20eventually%20give%20AMC%20a%20row%20on%20its%20powerful%20homepage%C2%A0%E2%80%94%20the%20kind%20they%20use%20now%2C%20with%20labeling%20that's%20either%20super-generic%20(%26quot%3BBlockbuster%20Movies%26quot%3B)%20or%20embarrassingly%20detailed%20(%26quot%3BBecause%20you%20watched%20'The%20Equalizer'%26quot%3B).%20At%20least%20for%20some%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20again%2C%20I'm%20a%20user%20who%20watches%20AMC%20shows%2C%20so%20you'd%20think%20they%20would%20get%20this%20to%20me%20quite%20soon%2C%20if%20not%20already.%20And%20it's%20one%20thing%20to%20give%20AMC%20a%20row%20%E2%80%94%20quite%20another%20to%20put%20it%20somewhere%20where%20you%20can%20find%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Netflix%20rep%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20until%20I%20hear%20or%20see%20otherwise%2C%20I'm%20finding%20it%20hard%20to%20believe%20Netflix%20will%20dedicate%20meaningful%20screen%20space%20to%20a%20single%20provider%2C%20even%20if%20they%20give%20Netflix%20really%20good%20stuff%20like%20%26quot%3BBreaking%20Bad.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-wins-streaming-wars-this-chart-shows-why-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENetflix%20now%20has%20the%20upper%20hand%20with%20the%20TV%20guys%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Hard%20to%20see%20why%20they'd%20make%20any%20concessions%2C%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E*Yes%2C%20it's%20a%20stressful%20job!%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjon-stewart-daily-show-audience-old-small-tv-ratings-streaming-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIn%20a%20declining%20industry%3C%2Fa%3E!%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20%3