ss%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20committed%20to%20(or%20even%20a%20little%20obsessive%20about)%20your%20produce%20and%20meat%20being%20as%20fresh%20as%20possible%2C%20why%20should%20your%20coffee%20be%20any%20different%3F%20Brooklyn-based%20roaster%20Devoci%C3%B3n%20works%20with%20Colombian%20growers%2C%20who%20harvest%20coffee%20year-round.%20The%20service%20claims%20%26quot%3Bfaster%20transport%20from%20origin%20to%20cup%20than%20any%20other%20purveyor%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20can%20be%20in%20as%20little%20as%2010%20days.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDevoci%C3%B3n's%20coffees%20are%20flavorful%2C%20balanced%2C%20and%20unlike%20anything%20else%20on%20the%20market%2C%20thanks%20to%20its%20unique%20supplier%20relationships.%20The%20subscriptions%20are%20to%20individual%20blends%20(you%20can%20take%20a%20quiz%20on%20your%20preferences%20to%20be%20matched%20to%20your%20ideal%20blend)%2C%20unlike%20other%20roasters%20offering%20subscriptions%20with%20more%20variety%2C%20but%20the%20coffee%20is%20next-level%20enough%20that%20it's%20worth%20considering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20a%20coffee%20subscription%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20working%20in%20the%20specialty%20food%20world%20since%202015%2C%20eating%2C%20drinking%2C%20learning%2C%20teaching.%20For%20these%20rankings%2C%20I%20tasted%20through%20the%20available%20coffee%20subscriptions%2C%20both%20from%20roasters%20and%20otherwise.%20This%20is%20what%20I%20was%20looking%20for%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFlavor%20and%20quality%20of%20the%20beans%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETastes%20vary%2C%20but%20there%20are%20some%20objective%20flaws%20in%20coffee%20beans%2C%20such%20as%20beans%20tasting%20burnt.%20This%20was%20less%20about%20how%20much%20I%20liked%20each%20selection%20personally%20and%20more%20about%20how%20balanced%20the%20coffees%20were%20and%20whether%20they%20matched%20their%20flavor%20notes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEase%20of%20setup%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ECoffee%20and%20subscription%20services%20should%2