%20ready%20to%20compromise%20are%20given%20code%20names%2C%20and%20those%20who%20are%20not%20ready%20to%20yield%20are%20pushed%20out%20of%20the%20field%2C%20as%20per%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20highlighted%20the%20widespread%20nature%20of%20the%20issue%2C%20sparking%20concerns%20about%20the%20safety%20and%20well-being%20of%20women%20in%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20come%20out%20in%20evidence%20that%20certain%20men%20in%20cinema%2C%20who%20are%20well-known%20and%20well-reputed%20for%20their%20ability%20as%20artist%2C%20director%20or%20whoever%20he%20be%20in%20the%20film%20industry%20have%20shocked%20certain%20women%20in%20cinema%20by%20sexual%20harassment%20and%20physical%20advances%20made%20by%20them%20towards%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20expert%20panel%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20copy%20of%20the%20report%20was%20given%20to%20the%20media%20under%20the%20RTI%20Act%20after%20five%20years%20of%20its%20submission%20to%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20series%20of%20shocking%20and%20shameful%20revelations%2C%20the%20report%20stated%20that%20female%20actors%20faced%20harassment%2C%20including%20instances%20where%20the%20doors%20of%20their%20rooms%20were%20knocked%20on%20by%20intoxicated%20individuals%20in%20the%20film%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20them%2C%20who%20suffered%20sexual%20harassment%2C%20were%20reluctant%20to%20complain%20about%20this%20to%20the%20police%20due%20to%20fear%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20sky%20is%20full%20of%20mysteries%2C%20with%20the%20twinkling%20stars%20and%20the%20beautiful%20moon.%20But%20scientific%20investigation%20revealed%20that%20the%20stars%20do%20not%20twinkle%2C%20nor%20does%20the%20moon%20look%20beautiful%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDo%20not%20trust%20what%20you%20see%3B%20even%20salt%20looks%20like%20sugar%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20opening%20lines%20of%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20report%2C%20submitted%20by%20the%20three-member%20panel%2C%20the%20major%20issue%20which%20women%20face%20in%20the%20film%20industry%20is%20sexual%20harassment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20the%20worst%20evil%20which%20women%20in%20cinema%20face%20in%20the%20film%20industry.%20The%20women%20in%20cinema%20are%20most%20reluctant%20to%20speak%20out%20about%20the%20sexual%20harassment%20which%20they%20are%20subjected%20to%2C%20even%20to%20other%20women%20or%20close%20relatives%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20commission%20said%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bshocked%20to%20hear%20the%20sexual%20harassment%20stories%26quot%3B%20revealed%20to%20it%20by%20women%20working%20in%20the%20Malayalam%20film%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20offer%20to%20act%20or%20for%20doing%20any%20other%20job%20in%20cinema%20comes%20to%20a%20woman%20coupled%20with%20demand%20for%20sexual%20favours.%20As%20I%20already%20mentioned%2C%20the%20woman%20would%20be%20asked%20to%20adjust%20and%20compromise%2C%20thereby%20she%20is%20asked%20to%20surrender%20to%20sexual%20demands%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20most%20of%20the%20hotels%2C%20where%20they%20are%20staying%2C%20the%20doors%20are%20knocked%20by%20the%20men%20working%20in%20cinema%20who%20could%20be%20mostly%20under%20intoxication.%20Many%20women%20have%20stated%20that%20knocking%20will%20not%20be%20polite%20or%20decent%20but%2C%20they%20repeatedly%20bang%20the%20door%20by%20force%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20detailed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20panel%20said%20even%20though%20many%20sexual%20acts%20committed%20against%20women%20in%20cinema%20come%20under%20the%20IPC%20and%20under%20the%20definition%20of%20the%20Sexual%20Harassment%20of%20Women%20at%20Workplace%20(Prevention%2C%20prohibition%20and%20redressal)%20Act%20(POSH)%2C%20the%20women%20who%20suffered%20the%20atrocities%20prefer%20to%20keep%20silence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20artist%20added%20that%20if%20they%20take%20up%20the%20matter%20before%20the%20court%20or%20the%20police%2C%20they%20will%20face%20worse%20consequences%2C%20including%20threat%20to%20life.%20The%20artist%20added%20that%20threat%20to%20life%20will%20not%20only%20be%20against%20the%20victims%20but%20even%20their%20close%20family%20members%20will%20be%20in%20danger%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20has%20categorically%20mentioned%20that%20the%20police%20should%20register%20FIRs%20against%20crimes%20that%20are%20being%20committed%20in%20the%20industry%2C%20and%20many%20are%20not%20coming%20out%20fearing%20for%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20publication%20of%20the%20report%2C%20initially%20scheduled%20for%20July%2024%2C%20was%20put%20on%20hold%20by%20the%20Kerala%20High%20Court%20following%20a%20plea%20from%20a%20Malayalam%20film%20producer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20later%20dismissed%20the%20plea%20on%20August%2013%20and%20directed%20the%20government%20to%20release%20the%20report%20within%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20publication%20was%20delayed%20again%20due%20to%20a%20plea%20from%20an%20actress%2C%20which%20was%20heard%20by%20the%20High%20Court%20on%20Monday.%20The%20government%20finally%20released%20the%20report%20on%20Monday%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20Cultural%20Affairs%20Minister%20Saji%20Cheriyan%20said%20the%20government%20has%20taken%20note%20of%20the%20findings%20and%20recommendations%20of%20the%20Justice%20Hema%20Committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20would%20convene%20a%20cinema%20conclave%20in%20the%20next%20two%20months%20to%20discuss%20and%20resolve%20the%20issues%20in%20the%20film%20industry%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20Congress%20expressed%20shock%20over%20the%20findings%20of%20the%20committee%20and%20sought%20to%20know%20whom%20the%20government%20tried%20to%20protect%20by%20keeping%20the%20report%20without%20releasing%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20action%20of%20the%20government%20and%20the%20chief%20minister%20who%20kept%20the%20report%20in%20cold%20storage%20so%20far%20was%20a%20criminal%20offence%2C%26quot%3B%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20in%20the%20State%20Assembly%20V%20D%20Satheesan%20told%20reporters%20in%20Kochi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EActor%20Siddique%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20president%20of%20actor%20outfit%20AMMA%2C%20said%20they%20would%20study%20the%20report%20in%20detail%20and%20take%20necessary%20steps%20to%20address%20the%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWomen%20in%20Cinema%20Collective%2C%20an%20outfit%20of%20women%20professionals%20in%20the%20industry%2C%20expressed%20happiness%20over%20the%20releasing%20of%20the%20report%20and%20thanked%20the%20panel%20members%2C%20media%2C%20women%20organisations%20and%20the%20lawyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724092260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-08%2F554nh7ro_she-has-filed-a-police-case-alleging-sexual-harassment-representative-image_625x300_18_August_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpanel-report-reveals-stories-of-harassment-women-face-in-malayalam-cinema-6373413%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20much-awaited%20Justice%20Hema%20Committee%20report%20on%20harassment%20faced%20by%20women%20in%20the%20Malayalam%20cinema%20industry%20has%20recorded%20explosive%20accounts%20of%20harassment%2C%20exploitation%20and%20ill-treatment%20of%20female%20professionals.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpanel-report-reveals-stories-of-harassment-women-face-in-malayalam-cinema-6373413%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Migrant%20workers%20on%20Scottish%20fishing%20b