nt%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fbox-office%2Fstree-2-box-office-collection-day-5-shraddha-kapoor-rajkummar-raos-film-rides-raksha-bandhan-wave-set-to-earn-rs-37-crore%2Farticleshow%2F112634584.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CBI%20Veterans%20Of%20Hathras%2C%20Unnao%20Take%20Charge%20Of%20Kolkata%20Rape-Murder%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20responsibility%20of%20the%20investigation%20into%20the%20Kolkata%20doctor's%20rape-murder%20case%2C%20has%20been%20handed%20over%20to%20two%20of%20the%20CBI's%20top%20women%20officers%2C%20who%20have%20handled%20a%20few%20such%20notorious%20cases%20earlier%2C%20with%20considerable%20success.%20The%20overall%20charge%20belongs%20Sampat%20Meena%2C%20a%201994%20batch%20IPS%20officer%20from%20Jharkhand%2C%20who%20handled%20the%20Hathras%20rape-murder%20case%20and%20the%20Unnao%20rape%20case.%20With%20her%20is%20officer%20Seema%20Pahuja%2C%20who%20was%20also%20part%20of%20the%20Hathras%20investigation%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Meena%2C%20an%20Additional%20Director%2C%20is%20now%20in%20charge%20of%20a%20team%20of%2025%20officers%2C%20and%20will%20work%20in%20a%20supervisory%20capacity.%20The%20ground%20level%20investigation%20will%20be%20carried%20out%20by%20Ms%20Pahuja%2C%20an%20Additional%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%2C%20has%20received%20the%20Gold%20Medal%20twice%20for%20excellent%20investigation%20between%202007%20and%202018.%20The%20officer%2C%20who%20wanted%20to%20take%20VRS%20once%20due%20to%20family%20responsibilities%2C%20was%20persuaded%20by%20then%20CBI%20Director%20not%20to%20quit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20Ms%20Pahuja%20achieved%20a%20conviction%20is%20what%20was%20till%20then%20regarded%20as%20a%20blind%20case%20--%20the%20rape-murder%20of%20a%20Class%2010%20student%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Gudiya%20case%20of%202017%20had%20seared%20the%20hill%20state.%20The%20teen%20went%20missing%20while%20returning%20from%20school%20--%20the%20path%20went%20through%20a%20dense%20forest%20track%20where%20she%20was%20abducted.%20Her%20body%20was%20found%20two%20days%20later.%20She%20had%20been%20raped%20and%20strangled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnil%20Kumar%2C%20a%20woodcutter%2C%20was%20found%20guilty%20and%20sentenced%20to%20sentenced%20to%20life%20imprisonment%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20April%202018%2C%20the%20CBI%20had%20revealed%20how%20it%20cracked%20the%20case%20--%20using%20advanced%20DNA%20technology%20of%20percentage%20and%20lineage%20matching.%20After%20questioning%20over%201000%20locals%2C%20they%20finally%20tested%20the%20DNA%20of%20over%20250%20people%20and%20found%20a%20match%20to%20forensic%20samples%20in%20the%20father%20of%20the%20accused.%20The%20son%2C%20who%20was%20out%20on%20bail%20and%20on%20the%20run%2C%20was%20later%20traced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202017%20Unnao%20rape%20case%20too%2C%20the%20team%20had%20secured%20a%20conviction.%20BJP%20leader%20and%20local%20MLA%20Kuldeep%20Singh%20Sengar%20--%20who%20was%20later%20expelled%20from%20the%20party%20--%20was%20given%20life%20term%20in%20jail%20for%20the%20gangrape%20of%20a%2017-year-old%20Dalit%20girl.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20also%20found%20guilty%20of%20the%20death%20of%20the%20girl's%20father%20in%20judicial%20custody%2C%20for%20which%20he%20is%20serving%20a%2010-year%20jail%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202020%20Hathras%20case%2C%20which%20also%20generated%20headlines%20across%20the%20country%2C%20sparking%20massive%20public%20outrage%2C%20a%2019-year-old%20girl%20was%20allegedly%20assaulted%20and%20gang-raped%20by%20four%20men%20of%20the%20so-called%20upper%20caste.%20A%20fortnight%20later%2C%20she%20succumbed%20to%20her%20injuries%20in%20Delhi's%20Safdarjung%20Hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20added%20to%20the%20public%20outrage%20was%20that%20her%20body%20was%20cremated%20by%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Police%20and%20the%20administration%20allegedly%20without%20the%20consent%20or%20the%20presence%20of%20her%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20of%20the%20four%20accused%20in%20the%20case%20have%20walked%20free.%20The%20fourth%2C%20Sandeep%20Thakur%2C%20has%20been%20convicted%20for%20culpable%20homicide%20not%20amounting%20to%20murder%2C%20and%20not%20of%20rape%20or%20murder.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20had%20based%20its%20judgment%20on%20the%20mismatch%20between%20the%20woman's%20statement%20and%20the%20forensic%20evidence.%20The%20police%20had%20claimed%20there%20was%20no%20evidence%20of%20rape%20and%20the%20woman%20had%20died%20of%20a%20neck%20injury.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20police%20were%20accused%20of%20massive%20lapses%20at%20every%20stage%20of%20the%20case%20--%20starting%20with%20the%20delay%20in%20filing%20of%20the%20First%20Information%20Report%2C%20then%20denial%20of%20rape%20and%20the%20hurried%20cremation%20of%20the%20body.%20In%20face%20of%20the%20public%20outrage%2C%20on%20October%203%2C%202020%2C%20the%20state%20government%20had%20suspended%20five%20police%20officers%20including%20the%20Superintendent%20of%20Police.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724090580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F9ckqi2ho_rg-kar-doctors-candle-march-ani_625x300_11_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frg-kar-cbi-veterans-of-hathras-unnao-take-charge-of-kolkata-rape-murder-case-6372454%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20responsibility%20of%20the%20investigation%20into%20the%20Kolkata%20doctor's%20rape-murder%20case%2C%20has%20been%20handed%20over%20to%20two%20of%20the%20CBI's%20top%20women%20officers%2C%20who%20have%20handled%20a%20few%20such%20notorious%20cases%20earlier%2C%20with%20considerable%20success.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frg-kar-cbi-veterans-of-hathras-unnao-take-charge-of-kolkata-rape-murder-case-6372454%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BMy%20Intention%20Was%20To...%26quot%3B%3A%20Sudha%20Murty%20Clarifies%20Raksha%20Bandhan%20Post%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Sudha%20Murty%20shared%20a%20message%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20Raksha%20Bandhan%20and%20explained%20how%20it%20is%20an%20%26quot%3Bimportant%20festival%26quot%3B%20for%20her%20and%20the%20value%20a%20thread%20or%20rakhi%20holds.%20The%20Infosys%20Chairman's%20wife%20also%20shared%20the%20story%20behind%20the%20festival%2C%20which%20sparked%20a%20debate%20on%20social%20media%20platform%20X%2C%20with%20users%20differing%20from%20her.%20She%20later%20issued%20a%20clarification%20and%20said%20he%20intention%20was%20to%20highlight%20one%20of%20the%20many%20stories%20she%20learnt%20about%20when%20growing%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRaksha%20Bandha%20is%20an%20important%20festival%20for%20me%2C%20where%20a%20sister%20ties%20a%20thread%20indicating%20that%20in%20case%20of%20any%20difficulty%2C%20you%20should%20always%20be%20there%20to%20help%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20a%20video%20message%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ERaksha%20Bandhan%20has%20a%20rich%20history.%20When%20Rani%20Karnavati%20was%20in%20danger%2C%20she%20sent%20a%20thread%20to%20King%20Humayun%20as%20a%20symbol%20of%20sibling-hood%2C%20asking%20for%20his%20help.%20This%20is%20where%20the%20tradition%20of%20the%20thread%20began%20and%20it%20continues%20to%20this%20day.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fp98lwCZ6Pp%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fp98lwCZ6Pp%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Smt.%20Sudha%20Murty%20(%40SmtSudhaMurty)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSmtSudhaMurty%2Fstatus%2F1825374632331141397%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2019%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20wife%20of%20the%20Infosys%20Chairman%20shared%20the%20story%20behind%20the%20festival%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20goes%20back%20to%20when%20Rani%20Karnavati%20(from%20the%20Kingdom%20of%20Mewar)%20was%20in%20danger%20after%20her%20kingdom%2C%20which%20was%20small%2C%20came%20under%20attack.%20She%20did%20not%20know%20what%20to%20do.%20She%20sent%20a%20small%20piece%20of%20thread%20to%20Mughal%20Emperor%20Humayun%20and%20said%20I'm%20in%20danger%20please%20consider%20me%20as%20your%20sister.%20Please%20do%20come%20and%20protect%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Murty%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHumayun%20did%20not%20know%20what%20it%20was...he%20asked%20what%20is%20this%20and%20the%20locals%20said%20this%20is%20a%20call%20of%20a%20sister%20to%20a%20brother...this%20is%20the%20custom%20of%20the%20land%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20emperor%20said%20okay%20if%20this%20is%20the%20case%20then%20I%20will%20help%20Rani%20Karnavati.%20He%20left%20Delhi%20but%20couldn't%20reach%20there%20on%20time%20and%20Karnavati%20died.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20idea%20is%20when%20you're%20facing%20a%20threat%20or%20in%20distress.%20A%20thread%20indicates%20that%20somebody%20should%20come%20and%20help%20me%20and%20it%20means%20a%20lot...%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20several%20users%20on%20X%20differed%20and%20said%20the%20story%20goes%20back%20to%20the%20time%20of%20Mahabharat%20and%20not%20post-medieval%20India.%20Users%20said%2C%20that%20during%20the%20time%20of%20Mahabharat%2C%20Lord%20Krishna%20inadvertently%20cut%20his%20finger%20while%20using%20the%20Sudarshan%20chakra%20to%20kill%20King%20Shishupal.%20Draupadi%20covered%20the%20wound%20with%20a%20piece%20of%20cloth.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-conversation%3D%5C%22none%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EWith%20absolute%20respect%20Madam%2C%20the%20origin%20of%20Rakshabandan%20dates%20back%20to%20the%20Mahabharata%20times.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnLord%20Krishna%20once%20accidentally%20cut%20his%20find%20on%20the%20Sudarshan%20Chakra.%20Seeing%20him%20injured%2C%20Draupadi%20tore%20a%20piece%20of%20cloth%20from%20her%20saree%20and%20tied%20it%20to%20stop%20the%20bleeding.%20Touched%20by%20her%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20D%20Prasanth%20Nair%20(%40DPrasanthNair)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDPrasanthNair%2Fstatus%2F1825406077502181580%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2019%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELord%20Krishna%20was%20touched%20by%20her%20deed%20and%20promised%20to%20keep%20her%20safe%20from%20any%20harm.%20During%20the%20Chirharan%20incident%2C%20when%20the%20Kauravas%20tried%20to%20shame%20and%20dishonour%20Draupadi%2C%20Lord%20Krishna%20appeared%20and%20protected%20her%20when%20no%20one%20else%20could.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20later%20issued%20a%20clarification%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20story%20I%20shared%20on%20Raksha%20Bandhan%20is%20just%20one%20of%20many%20tales%20associated%20with%20the%20festival%20and%20certainly%20not%20its%20origin.%20I%20mentioned%20in%20the%20video%20that%2C%20%26quot%3Bthis%20was%20already%20a%20custom%20of%20the%20land.%20My%20intention%20was%20to%20highlight%20one%20of%20the%20many%20stories%20I%20learnt%20about%20when%20growing%20up%2C%20about%20the%20beautiful%20symbolism%20behind%20Raksha%20Bandhan.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20story%20I%20shared%20on%20Raksha%20Bandhan%20is%20just%20one%20of%20many%20tales%20associated%20with%20the%20festival%20and%20certainly%20not%20its%20origin.%20As%20I%20have%20said%20in%20the%20video%20clip%2C%20this%20was%20already%20a%20custom%20of%20the%20land.%20My%20intention%20was%20to%20highlight%20one%20of%20the%20many%20stories%20I%20learnt%20about%20when%20growing%20up%2C%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Smt.%20Sudha%20Murty%20(%40SmtSudhaMurty)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSmtSudhaMurty%2Fstatus%2F1825533855593279771%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2019%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20several%20stories%20on%20the%20history%20of%20the%20festival%20including%20the%20story%20of%20King%20Bali%20and%20Goddess%20Lakshmi.%20King%20Bali%20was%20a%20staunch%20devotee%20of%20Lord%20Vishnu%20and%20he%20took%20the%20responsibility%20to%20protect%20Bali's%20Kingdom%20for%20which%20he%20left%20Vikundam.%20Goddess%20Lakshmi%20wanted%20to%20stay%20with%20her%20husband%20Lord%20Vishnu.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20tied%20Rakhi%20on%20King%20Bali's%20wrist%20on%20the%20full%20moon%20day%20called%20Shravana%20Purnima.%20It%20is%20believed%20that%20since%20that%20day%20onwards%20it%20has%20become%20a%20custom%20to%20invite%20one's%20sister%20on%20Shravana%20Purnima%20to%20tie%20an%20auspicious%20thread%20of%20Rakhi%20or%20Raksha%20Bandhan.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724090580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-05%2Fd544f28o_sudha-murty-parenting-tips_625x300_20_May_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsudha-murtys-raksha-bandhan-post-stirs-debate-on-x-what-she-said-6370651%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Sudha%20Murty%20shared%20a%20message%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20Raksha%20Bandhan%20and%20explained%20how%20it%20is%20an%20%26quot%3Bimportant%20festival%26quot%3B%20for%20her%20and%20the%20value%20a%20thread%20or%20rakhi%20holds.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsudha-murtys-raksha-bandhan-post-stirs-debate-on-x-what-she-said-6370651%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Salman%20to%20shoot%20with%2010%2C000