nister%20Hits%20Out%20At%20Rahul%20Gandhi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELaw%20Minister%20Arjun%20Ram%20Meghwal%20on%20Monday%20hit%20out%20at%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20for%20his%20claim%20that%20the%20government%20was%20trying%20to%20bypass%20the%20reservation%20system%20through%20lateral%20entry%2C%20reminding%20the%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20that%20former%20prime%20minister%20Manmohan%20Singh%20was%20made%20the%20finance%20secretary%20in%201976%20through%20the%20lateral%20entry%20route.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20also%20dismissed%20as%20%26quot%3Bbaseless%26quot%3B%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20allegation%20that%20RSS%20people%20will%20be%20hired%20as%20public%20servants%20through%20this%20mode%20and%20pointed%20out%20that%20it%20was%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20who%20made%20the%20system%20of%20lateral%20entry%20methodical%20by%20giving%20the%20mandate%20to%20UPSC%20for%20framing%20rules.%20Earlier%2C%20he%20pointed%20out%2C%20there%20was%20no%20formal%20system%20in%20place%20for%20such%20entry%20into%20governance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhatever%20appointments%20or%20recruitments%20or%20selections%20are%20to%20be%20done%2C%20UPSC%20will%20do%20it.%20Where%20is%20the%20issue%20of%20BJP%2C%20RSS%20in%20this%3F%20Baseless%20allegations%20are%20being%20made%2C%26quot%3B%20Arjun%20Meghwal%20told%20PTI%20Videos%20in%20Bikaner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20RSS%20is%20an%20organisation%20that%20promotes%20cultural%20nationalism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20alleged%20that%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20was%20trying%20to%20mislead%20people%20and%20tarnish%20the%20image%20of%20institutions%20like%20UPSC%20by%20%26quot%3Bspreading%20lies%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20efforts%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20is%20making%20such%20false%20allegations%2C%20are%20never%20going%20to%20succeed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20despite%20being%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20which%20is%20a%20constitutional%20post%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20was%20making%20irresponsible%20statements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDr%20Manmohn%20Singh%20was%20also%20part%20of%20the%20lateral%20entry.%20How%20did%20you%20directly%20make%20him%20the%20finance%20secretary%20in%201976%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20then%20Planning%20Commission%20deputy%20chairman%20Montek%20Singh%20Ahluwalia%20entered%20service%20through%20the%20lateral%20entry%20route.%20He%20said%20CPP%20chairperson%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20was%20made%20head%20of%20the%20National%20Advisory%20Council.%20%26quot%3BThe%20prime%20minister's%20is%20a%20constitutional%20post.%20But%20is%20NAC%20a%20constitutional%20body%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20quipped%20adding%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20was%20placed%20above%20the%20prime%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20alleged%20the%20then%20prime%20minister%20Jawahar%20Lal%20Nehru%20had%20opposed%20reservation%20in%201961%20and%20as%20the%20leader%20of%20opposition%2C%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20opposed%20OBC%20reservation%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20started%20lateral%20entry.%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20made%20it%20methodical%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20noted%20that%20these%20are%20contractual%20posts.%20%26quot%3BSuppose%20an%20environment%20expert%20becomes%20a%20deputy%20secretary%2C%20what%20is%20the%20problem...%20person%20has%20to%20be%20an%20expert%20in%20a%20particular%20field%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20lateral%20entry%20is%20open%20to%20all.%20%26quot%3BPersons%20of%20SC%2C%20ST%20and%20OBC%20categories%20also%20apply.%20IAS%20vacancies%20are%20different.%20They%20claim%20we%20are%20ending%20reservations.%20What%20were%20you%20doing%20when%20you%20were%20recruiting%3F%20Suddenly%20their%20love%20for%20OBCs%20has%20come%20out.%20They%20are%20trying%20to%20mislead%20SC%2C%20ST%2C%20OBC%20students%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECondemning%20the%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20a%20junior%20doctor%20in%20Kolkata%2C%20he%20said%20that%20the%20whole%20country%20is%20ashamed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20the%20incident%2C%20efforts%20were%20made%20to%20destroy%20the%20evidence.%20It%20is%20a%20very%20shameful%20incident%20and%20we%20condemn%20it%20in%20very%20strong%20words%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20Arjun%20Meghwal%2C%20who%20is%20an%20MP%20from%20Bikaner%2C%20reached%20a%20BSF%20outpost%20in%20Khanuwali%20on%20the%20Indo-Pakistan%20border%20and%20celebrated%20the%20festival%20of%20Raksha%20Bandhan%20with%20women%20BSF%20personnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724088660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fe7jdg43_arjun-ram-meghwal_625x300_19_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmanmohan-singh-was-part-of-lateral-entry-law-minister-hits-out-at-rahul-gandhi-6373088%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Law%20Minister%20Arjun%20Ram%20Meghwal%20on%20Monday%20hit%20out%20at%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20reminding%20him%20that%20former%20prime%20minister%20Manmohan%20Singh%20was%20made%20the%20finance%20secretary%20in%201976%20through%20the%20lateral%20entry%20route.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmanmohan-singh-was-part-of-lateral-entry-law-minister-hits-out-at-rahul-gandhi-6373088%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Banks%20need%20to%20align%20credit%20and%20deposit%20growth%2C%20says%20RBI%20Bulletin%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724088649000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-08%2F19%2Fthumb%2Ff