9F%87%AE%F0%9F%87%B3%20(%40crpfindia)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcrpfindia%2Fstatus%2F1825559145451241788%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2019%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday's%20attack%20took%20place%20in%20the%20Jammu%20region%2C%20which%20for%20several%20years%2C%20remained%20relatively%20silent%20compared%20to%20Kashmir.%20There%20has%20been%20a%20spurt%20of%20terror%20activities%20in%20Jammu%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20southern%20reaches%20of%20the%20Pir%20Panjal%20range%2C%20which%20contains%20thick%20forests%20and%20steep%20mountains%20that%20provide%20cover%20for%20terrorists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERise%20In%20Terror%20Attacks%20In%20Jammu%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farmy-officer-injured-in-encounter-during-search-operation-in-j-ks-doda-6334173%5C%22%3EOn%20August%2014%2C%20an%20army%20officer%2C%20Captain%20Deepak%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20was%20killed%20in%20action%20after%20an%20encounter%20broke%20out%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20Doda.%20A%20civilian%20was%20also%20injured%20in%20the%20incident.%20The%20officer%20suffered%20gunshot%20wounds%20in%20a%20forested%20area%20during%20a%20cordon-and-search%20operation%20in%20the%20Shivgarh-Assar%20belt%20of%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20that%20day%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frajnath-singh-chairs-key-security-meet-over-rising-terror-attacks-in-j-k-6334916%5C%22%3EDefence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%20chaired%20a%20high-level%20meeting%20over%20rising%20terror%20attacks%20in%20the%20Union%20Territory%20after%20back-to-back%20encounters%20and%20ambushes%20took%20place.%20The%20meeting%20was%20held%20at%20the%20South%20Block%20in%20Delhi%2C%20with%20NSA%20Ajit%20Doval%20and%20Army%20Chief%20General%20Upendra%20Dwivedi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecent%20intelligence%20reports%20suggested%20that%20the%20terrorists%20may%20target%20highways%2C%20the%20lifeline%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20The%20Centre%20decided%20to%20deploy%20more%20troops%20from%20CRPF%20along%20with%20local%20police%20to%20patrol%20highways%20and%20adjacent%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2010%2C%20two%20soldiers%20and%20a%20civilian%20were%20killed%20during%20a%20gunfight%20between%20terrorists%20and%20security%20forces%20in%20Anantnag.%20The%20region%20has%20witnessed%20attacks%20on%20an%20army%20convoy%20in%20Kathua%2C%20skirmishes%20in%20Doda%20and%20Udhampur%2C%20and%20a%20failed%20attack%20by%20the%20Pakistan%20Border%20Action%20Team%20(BAT)%20along%20the%20Line%20of%20Control%20(LoC)%20in%20Kupwara%20district's%20Machchal%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20(MHA)%2C%2028%20people%2C%20including%20civilians%20and%20security%20personnel%2C%20were%20killed%20in%2011%20terror-related%20incidents%20and%2024%20counter-terror%20operations%20up%20to%20July%2021%20this%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAction%20Plan%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20official%20told%20NDTV%20that%20the%20increased%20military%20casualties%20are%20a%20significant%20concern%2C%20which%20has%20led%20to%20the%20rationalisation%20of%20force%20deployment%20in%20the%20area%20with%20new%20combinations%20and%20strategies.%20The%20government%2C%20while%20maintaining%20a%20focus%20on%20securing%20the%20Kashmir%20Valley%2C%20has%20also%20recognised%20the%20need%20to%20bolster%20security%20in%20the%20Jammu%20region.%20This%20has%20resulted%20in%20the%20mobilisation%20of%20additional%20forces%20for%20deployment%20in%20key%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20primary%20objectives%20of%20the%20government's%20new%20security%20strategy%20is%20to%20plug%20infiltration%20routes%20used%20by%20terrorists%20to%20enter%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecurity%20audits%20conducted%20by%20various%20agencies%20identified%20about%20two%20dozen%20sectors%20along%20the%20Line%20of%20Control%20(LOC)%20in%20the%20valley%20and%20the%20international%20border%20in%20the%20Jammu%20sector.%20Terrorists%20often%20take%20help%20from%20local%20guides%20to%20cross%20over.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20terrorists%20are%20equipped%20with%20sophisticated%20weapons%20like%20the%20American-made%20M4%20assault%20ride%20with%20an%20infrared%20thermal%20sight%20and%20are%20trained%20in%20jungle%20warfare.%20Terrorists%20infiltrate%20by%20foot%20and%20the%20government%20has%20initiated%20a%20project%20to%20fence%20the%20borders%20however%20the%20progress%20has%20been%20slow%20with%20only%2070%20kilometres%20being%20covered%20out%20of%20180%20kilometres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EElections%20In%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssembly%20Elections%20will%20be%20held%20in%20the%20Union%20Territory%20for%20the%20first%20time%20since%202014.%C2%A0Voting%20will%20be%20held%20in%20three%20phases%2C%20on%20September%2018%2C%20September%2025%2C%20and%20October%201%2C%20with%20results%20to%20be%20announced%20on%20October%204.%C2%A0This%20marks%20a%20big%20step%20forward%20in%20the%20poll%20body's%20efforts%20to%20meet%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20order%20-%20that%20democracy%20return%20to%20Jammu%2C%20and%20the%20Kashmir%20Valley%2C%20by%20September%2030.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724083260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fe4drg7a8_jammu-and-kashmir_625x300_16_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fparamilitary-soldier-killed-in-terror-attack-in-jammu-and-kashmirs-udhampur-6370984%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20soldier%20from%20the%20Central%20Reserve%20Police%20Force%20(CRPF)%20was%20killed%20in%20action%20after%20terrorists%20fired%20on%20a%20patrol%20party%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20Udhampur.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fparamilitary-soldier-ki