ans%20use%20tanks%20to%20destroy%20apartment%20buildings%20with%20little%20old%20ladies%20and%20kids%20just%20drove%20me%20crazy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Schmidt%2C%20who%20was%20Google's%20CEO%20from%202001%20to%202011%2C%20along%20with%20Sebastian%20Thrun%2C%20CEO%20of%20Udacity%2C%20is%20working%20on%20a%20new%20start%20up%20called%20White%20Stork.%20%26quot%3BThe%20idea%20basically%20is%20to%20do%20two%20things-%20use%20AI%20in%20complicated%2C%20powerful%20ways%20for%20these%20essentially%20robotic%20wars%20and%20the%20second%20one%20is%20to%20lower%20the%20cost%20of%20robots%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lecture%20Mr%20Schmidt%20delivered%20at%20Stanford%20in%20April%20was%20posted%20by%20the%20university%20on%20its%20YouTube%20last%20week%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20in%20Business%20Insider.%20The%20lecture%20quickly%20went%20viral%2C%20however%2C%20it%20was%20later%20taken%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20lecture%2C%20Mr%20Schmidt%20reportedly%20informed%20that%20White%20Stork%20will%20mass-produce%20drones%20equipped%20with%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20to%20identify%20targets%20to%20eliminate%20the%20need%20for%20ground%20battles%20with%20tanks%2C%20artillery%20and%20mortar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20clip%20of%20the%20lecture%2C%20now%20in%20wide%20circulation%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20twitter%2C%20Mr%20Schmidt%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20whole%20theory%20of%20armies%20is%20tanks%2C%20artilleries%20and%20mortar%20and%20we%20can%20eliminate%20all%20of%20them%2C%20and%20we%20can%20make%20the%20penalty%20for%20invading%20a%20country%2C%20at%20least%20by%20land%2C%20essentially%20be%20impossible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Schmidt%20said%20that%20he%20is%20now%20a%20licensed%20arms%20dealer%20%26quot%3Bbecause%20of%20the%20way%20the%20system%20works%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BA%20computer%20scientist%2C%20businessman%2C%20arms%20dealer.%20I%20do%20not%20recommend%20this%20in%20your%20career%20path%2C%20I'd%20stick%20with%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20of%20the%20way%20the%20laws%20work%2C%20we're%20doing%20this%20privately%20and%20this%20is%20all%20legal%20with%20the%20support%20of%20the%20government%2C%20so%20it%20goes%20straight%20into%20Ukraine%20and%20then%20they%20fight%20the%20war%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Russia-Ukraine%20war%2C%20which%20started%20in%20February%202022%2C%20has%20been%20going%20on%20for%20almost%20two%20and%20a%20half%20years%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20latest%20development%2C%20Ukrainian%20forces%20struck%20a%20third%20bridge%20in%20an%20attack%20on%20Russia's%20Kursk%20region.%20According%20to%20Ukraine%2C%20the%20ongoing%20offensive%20in%20the%20Kursk%20region%20is%20aimed%20at%20creating%20a%20%26quot%3Bbuffer%20zone%26quot%3B%20and%20to%20bring%20war%20closer%20to%20an%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20ongoing%20offensive%20in%20Kursk%20is%20said%20to%20be%20the%20biggest%20attack%20on%20Russia%20since%20World%20War%20II.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724082540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fenmvvahg_eric-schmidt_625x300_14_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-ukraine-war-has-turned-ex-google-ceo-eric-schmidt-into-licensed-arms-dealer-6372469%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20Google%20CEO%2C%20Eric%20Schmidt%2C%20has%20said%20that%20the%20Ukraine%20war%20has%20turned%20him%20into%20a%20licensed%20arms%20dealer.%20Mr%20Schmidt's%20new%20venture%20aims%20to%20converge%20AI%20and%20defense%20technology%20to%20help%20Ukraine%20fight%20in%20the%20ongoing%20war%20against%20Russia.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-ukraine-war-has-turned-ex-google-ceo-eric-schmidt-into-licensed-arms-dealer-6372469%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22