0during%20the%20pre-menstrual%C2%A0phase.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2029-year-old%20Vinesh%20was%20disqualified%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20the%20women's%2050kg%20freestyle%20final.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20on%20her%20appeal%20was%20rendered%20after%20three%20postponements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20appeal%2C%20Vinesh%20had%20demanded%20that%20she%20be%20given%20a%20joint%20silver%20with%20Cuban%20wrestler%20Yusneylis%20Guzman%20Lopez%2C%20who%20lost%20to%20her%20in%20the%20semifinals%20but%20was%20promoted%20to%20the%20summit%20clash%20following%20the%20Indian's%20disqualification.%20The%20gold%20was%20claimed%20by%20American%20Sarah%20Ann%20Hildebrandt.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724082360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fq3lks15_vinesh-phogat-afp_625x300_08_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fcas-gives-reasons-for-rejecting-vinesh-phogats-appeal-says-no-tolerance-6372401%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Court%20of%20Arbitration%20for%20Sport%20(CAS)%20has%20ruled%20that%20athletes%20will%20have%20to%20ensure%20that%20they%20remain%20below%20their%20weight%20limit%20and%20no%20exception%20can%20be%20provided%20under%20any%20circumstance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fcas-gives-reasons-for-rejecting-vinesh-phogats-appeal-says-no-tolerance-6372401%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Akshay%20Kumar's%20%E2%80%98Khel%20Khel%20Mein%E2%80%99%20CENSORED%20in%20UAE%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724082252000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112633060%2Cimgsize-30444.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fakshay-kumars-khel-khel-mein-censored-in-uae-fans-claim-fardeen-khans-character-arc-severely-affecte