mid%20enhanced%20surveillance%20for%20prompt%20detection.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOfficials%20said%20no%20mpox%20case%20has%20been%20reported%20from%20the%20country%20at%20present.%20According%20to%20assessment%2C%20the%20risk%20of%20a%20large%20outbreak%20with%20sustained%20transmission%20is%20low%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20World%20Health%20Organisation%20(WHO)%20has%20declared%20mpox%20a%20public%20health%20emergency%20of%20international%20concern%20in%20view%20of%20its%20prevalence%20and%20spread%20across%20many%20parts%20of%20Africa.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BThe%20virus%20strain%20this%20time%20is%20different%20and%20is%20more%20virulent%20and%20infectious.%20But%20the%20risk%20of%20a%20large%20outbreak%20with%20sustained%20transmission%20is%20low%20in%20the%20country%20as%20per%20the%20current%20assessment%2C%26quot%3B%20news%20agency%20PTI%20reported%20quoting%20an%20officer.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Health%20Ministry%20has%20ordered%20officials%20to%20ensure%20the%20network%20of%20testing%20laboratories%20is%20ready%20for%20early%20diagnosis%20of%20the%20disease.%20At%20present%2C%2032%20laboratories%20in%20the%20country%20are%20equipped%20for%20testing%20mpox.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAn%20earlier%20statement%20from%20WHO%20said%2099%2C176%20cases%20and%20208%20deaths%20have%20been%20reported%20due%20to%20mpox%20from%20116%20countries%20since%202022.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMpox%20cases%20have%20been%20steadily%20increasing%20in%20the%20Democratic%20Republic%20of%20Congo.%20Last%20year%2C%20the%20number%20of%20reported%20cases%20around%20the%20world%20increased%20significantly.%20This%20year%2C%20the%20number%20of%20cases%20reported%20so%20far%20has%20already%20exceeded%20last%20year's%20total%2C%20with%20more%20than%2015%2C600%20cases%20and%20537%20deaths.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESince%202022%2C%20at%20least%2030%20mpox%20cases%20have%20been%20reported%20from%20India.%20The%20last%20case%20of%20mpox%20was%20detected%20in%20March%20this%2