2%3A%22%3Cp%3EVinesh%20Phogat%20has%20seen%20a%20lot%20in%20the%20last%20fortnight.%20From%20the%20high%20of%20becoming%20the%20first%20Indian%20woman%20wrestler%20to%20enter%20an%20Olympics%20final%20to%20the%20low%20of%20getting%20disqualified%20for%20being%20100%20gram%20overweight%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20the%20gold%20medal%20bout%2C%20Vinesh%20has%20seen%20a%20lot.%20Her%20appeal%20for%20a%20shared%20silver%20medal%20was%20dismissed%20by%20the%20Court%20of%20Arbitration%20for%20Sport%20(CAS)%20too.%20The%20support%20and%20adulation%20for%20Vinesh%20has%20not%20been%20short%20though.%20From%20the%20time%20she%20landed%20in%20India%20from%20Paris%2C%20Vinesh%20has%20been%20showered%20with%20love%20wherever%20she%20has%20gone.%20There%20have%20been%20announcements%20of%20cash%20prize%20too.%20However%2C%20her%20husband%20Somvir%20Rathee%20has%20claimed%20that%20few%20organisations%20have%20made%20the%20false%20claims%20of%20giving%20her%20cash%20prize%20of%20ober%20Rs%2016%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVinesh%20Phogat%20has%20not%20received%20any%20money%20from%20the%20following%20organizations%2C%20businessmen%2C%20companies%20and%20parties.%20All%20of%20you%20are%20our%20well-wishers%2C%20please%20do%20not%20spread%20false%20news.%20This%20will%20not%20only%20harm%20us%20but%20will%20also%20harm%20social%20values.%20This%20is%20just%20a%20means%20to%20gain%20cheap%20popularity%2C%26quot%3B%20Rathee%20wrote%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22hi%5C%22%3E.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FziUaA8ct1W%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FziUaA8ct1W%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Somvir%20Rathee%20(%40somvir_rathee)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsomvir_rathee%2Fstatus%2F1825170958748922294%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2018%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3ECelebrated%20wrestler%C2%A0Vinesh%C2%A0Phogat%C2%A0on%20Saturday%20received%20a%20grand%20welcome%20on%20her%20return%20to%20the%20country%20with%20hundreds%20of%20supporters%20gathering%20outside%20the%20IGI%20airport%2C%20showing%20immense%20solidarity%20with%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStars%20such%20as%20Bajrang%20Punia%2C%20Sakshi%20Malik%20and%20panchayat%20leaders%20received%C2%A0Vinesh%2C%20who%20endured%20a%20heartbreaking%20exit%20at%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%20where%20she%20was%20disqualified%20for%20being%20overweight%20on%20the%20day%20of%20her%2050kg%20final.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeavily%20garlanded%2C%C2%A0Vinesh%C2%A0stood%20in%20an%20open%20Jeep%20and%20thanked%20all%20the%20supporters.%20Congress%20leader%20Deepender%20Hooda%20accompanied%C2%A0Vinesh%C2%A0and%20offered%20her%20sweets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20thank%20the%20entire%20country%20for%20support%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20her%20hands%20folded%20in%20humility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20thick%20security%20cover%20as%C2%A0Vinesh%2C%20who%20was%20found%20100%20grams%20overweight%20at%20the%20Olympics%2C%20landed%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVinesh's%20caravan%20left%20for%20her%20native%20village%20Balali%20in%20Haryana%20and%20on%20the%20way%20she%20met%20her%20supporters%2C%20positioned%20at%20different%20spots.%20Hooda%20presented%20a%20mace%2C%20a%20'symbol%20of%20victory'%20to%C2%A0Vinesh%2C%20who%20got%20emotional%20and%20was%20consoled%20by%20her%20husband%20Somvir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20PTI%20inputs%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724075700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fnb0rton_vinesh-phogat-husband-somvir-insta_625x300_19_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fgain-cheap-popularity-vinesh-phogats-husband-blasts-claims-of-rs-16-crore-plus-cash-prize-after-olympics-2024-6370774%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22From%20the%20high%20of%20becoming%20the%20first%20Indian%20woman%20wrestler%20to%20enter%20an%20Olympics%20final%20to%20the%20low%20of%20getting%20disqualified%20for%20being%20100%20gram%20overweight%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20the%20gold%20medal%20bout%2C%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20has%20seen%20a%20lot%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fgain-cheap-popularity-vinesh-phogats-husband-blasts-claims-of-rs-16-crore-plus-cash-prize-after-olympics-2024-6370774%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Inspired%20By%20Tagore%E2%80%99s%20Santiniketan%2C%20Bengal%20Man%20Starts%20%E2%80%98Tree%20School%E2%80%99%3B%20Innovates%20to%20Stop%20Dropouts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBiplab%2C%20a%20class%208%20student%20in%20the%20Bagdabra%20forest%20area%20in%20Murshidabad%2C%20West%20Bengal%2C%20is%20a%20first-generation%20learner.%20Studying%20in%20the%20government%20school%20nearby%2C%20the%20COVID-19%20lockdown%20was%20a%20big%20blow%20for%20young%20Biplab%20and%20his%20friends.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20the%20tribal%20community%2C%20many%20students%20like%20Biplab%20started%20going%20to%20work%20with%20their%20parents%20as%20schools%20were%20shut.%20Access%20to%20online%20classes%20was%20a%20distant%20dream%20for%20these%20children%2C%20where%20basic%20resources%20remain%20out%20of%20reach.%20With%20no%20guidance%2C%20a%20hand-to-mouth%20existence%20forced%20these%20children%20to%20ultimately%20drop%20out%2C%20with%20schools%20remaining%20shut%20for%20almost%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tribal%20communities%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20afford%20the%20luxury%20of%20virtual%20lessons.%20Near%20their%20village%2C%20even%20before%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20regular%20tree%20plantation%20drives%20were%20being%20conducted.%20These%20expanses%20of%20green%20attracted%20the%20children%2C%20making%20them%20regular%20visitors%20at%20the%20site.%20As%20luck%20would%20have%20it%2C%20the%20person%20conducting%20these%20tree%20plantations%20was%20a%20teacher%20by%20the%20name%20of%20Angshuman%20Thakur.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoticing%20the%20trend%20of%20school%20dropouts%20and%20seeing%20the%20children%20accompany%20their%20parents%20to%20work%20deeply%20moved%20the%2040-year-old.%20Since%20their%20schools%20provided%20mid-day%20meals%20to%20children%2C%20Angshuman%20first%20started%20providing%20the%20same%20to%20a%20group%20of%20five.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20the%20meals%2C%20he%20also%20served%20them%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F330978%2Fkamlesh-atwal-started-nanakmatta-public-school-uttarakhand-holistic-education-for-students%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espoonfuls%20of%20knowledge%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethrough%20his%20open%20air%20classes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20alumna%20of%20Visva%20Bharati%20University%20in%20Santikentan%2C%20he%20imbibed%20the%20principles%20of%20Rabindranath%20Tagore%20by%20providing%20a%20holistic%20education%20in%20sync%20with%20nature%2C%20which%20goes%20beyond%20merely%20words%20written%20in%20textbooks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarted%20with%20five%20children%20in%202021%2C%20today%20over%20105%20children%20study%20at%20Angshuman%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Anirvana%20Gacher%20Iskul%E2%80%99%20(Anirvana%20means%20inextinguishable%20and%20Gach%20means%20tree).%20Running%20on%20the%20benevolence%20of%20kind%20strangers%20and%20his%20own%20savings%2C%20it%20costs%20Rs%20300%20per%20month%20to%20educate%20a%20child%20in%20this%20school%20under%20a%20tree.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELearning%20in%20the%20lap%20of%20nature%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAngshuman%20works%20as%20a%20Bengali%20literature%20professor%20at%20Prof%20Syed%20Nurul%20Hasan%20College%20in%20Farakka%2C%20Murshidabad.%20Raised%20in%20the%20lap%20of%20nature%20and%20inspired%20by%20Tagore%E2%80%99s%20teachings%2C%20he%20pursued%20his%20higher%20studies%20at%20Visva%20Bharati%20univer