%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fmurugappa-group-fy24-results-net-profit-rises-15-2-to-rs-7-885-crore-124081900827_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fmurugappa-group-fy24-results-net-profit-rises-15-2-to-rs-7-885-crore-124081900827_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNo%20Ifs%20And%20Buts%26quot%3B%3A%20Chirag%20Paswan%20Wants%20Quota%20In%20UPSC%20Lateral%20Entry%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECongress's%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20found%20an%20unexpected%20ally%20in%20Union%20minister%20Chirag%20Paswan%2C%20who%20has%20become%20first%20NDA%20partner%20to%20criticize%20the%20lateral%20entry%20in%20the%20Union%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20or%20UPSC.%20Echoing%20Mr%20Gandhi's%20criticism%20that%20the%20lateral%20entry%20without%20quota%20deprives%20the%20disadvantaged%20communities%2C%20Mr%20Paswan%20said%20he%20would%20raise%20the%20issue%20with%20the%20Centre.%20His%20party%2C%20he%20added%2C%20is%20absolutely%20not%20in%20support%20of%20such%20a%20measure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BReservation%20provisions%20must%20be%20there%20in%20any%20government%20appointment.%20There%20are%20no%20ifs%20and%20buts%20in%20this.%20No%20reservation%20exists%20in%20the%20private%20sector%20and%20if%20it%20is%20not%20implemented%20in%20government%20positions%20as%20well...%20The%20information%20came%20up%20before%20me%20on%20Sunday%20and%20it%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20concern%20for%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20news%20agency%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lok%20Janshakti%20Party%20(Ram%20Vilas)%20chief%20said%20as%20a%20member%20of%20the%20government%2C%20he%20has%20the%20platform%20to%20raise%20the%20issue%20and%20he%20would.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20the%20UPSC%20had%20advertised%20for%20recruits%20to%20fill%2045%20posts%20--%2010%20of%20joint%20secretaries%20and%2035%20of%20directors%2Fdeputy%20secretaries%20--%20through%20the%20lateral%20entry%20on%20a%20contract%20basis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20has%20been%20shredded%20by%20the%20Congress%2C%20who%20called%20it%20a%20ploy%20to%20snatch%20jobs%20from%20disadvantaged%20classes%20and%20give%20it%20to%20cadres%20of%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20or%20RSS%2C%20the%20BJP's%20ideological%20mentor.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20Congress%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20(SP)%20and%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP)%20have%20alleged%20that%20it%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bconspiracy%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20BJP%20to%20appoint%20its%20ideological%20allies%20to%20high%20posts%20through%20the%20back%20door.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20claimed%20that%20while%20the%20UPA%20government%20introduced%20lateral%20entry%20to%20appoint%20select%20experts%20in%20some%20areas%2C%20the%20NDA%20government%20is%20using%20it%20to%20%26quot%3Bsnatch%20the%20rights%26quot%3B%20of%20Dalits%2C%20tribals%20and%20backward%20classes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSC%2C%20ST%2C%20OBC%2C%20EWS%20posts%20will%20now%20be%20given%20to%20people%20of%20the%20RSS.%20This%20is%20BJP's%20'Chakravyuh'%20to%20change%20the%20Constitution%20by%20snatching%20reservation%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kharge%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInformation%20and%20Broadcasting%20Minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20had%20said%20the%20Congress'%20criticism%20of%20the%20lateral%20entry%20system%20exposes%20its%20%26quot%3Bhypocrisy%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%2C%20Mr%20Vaishnaw%20said.%20%26quot%3BINC%20(Indian%20National%20Congress)%20hypocrisy%20is%20evident%20on%20lateral%20entry%20matter.%20It%20was%20the%20UPA%20government%20which%20developed%20the%20concept%20of%20lateral%20entry%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724073660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.co