0in%20arts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20in%201975%20when%20he%20returned%20to%20his%20home%20city%2C%20it%20was%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20learning.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20met%20so%20many%20blind%20people%20who%20did%20not%20have%20the%20same%20opportunities%20I%20had%20had%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%20This%20thought%20led%20Laljibhai%20to%20formally%20register%20what%20had%20started%20as%20an%20idea%20%E2%80%94%20Shri%20Navchetan%20Andhjan%20Mandal%20%E2%80%94%20in%201997.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fold-age-home_11zon-1723031030.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20old%20age%20home%20has%20seen%20over%20500%20senior%20citizens%20to%20date.%20These%20include%20both%20disabled%20and%20abled%20seniors%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fold-age-home_11zon-1723031030.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fold-age-home_11zon-1723031030-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fold-age-home_11zon-1723031030-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fold-age-home_11zon-1723031030-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fold-age-home_11zon-1723031030-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360212%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20old%20age%20home%20has%20seen%20over%20500%20senior%20citizens%20to%20date.%20These%20include%20both%20disabled%20and%20abled%20seniors.%20Picture%20source%3A%20Himanshu%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAn%20extended%20hand%20to%20blind%20seniors%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3