%20in%20broad%20daylight%20in%20Maharashtra.%20The%20incident%20happened%20yesterday%20at%20around%201%3A30%20pm%20in%20Kolhapur's%20Jaysingpur%20area%20and%20was%20captured%20on%20CCTV.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fcities%2Fvideo-maharashtra-woman-saves-sons-life-chases-away-3-men-who-attacked-him-6370637%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BMamata%20The%20Destroyer%26quot%3B%3A%20BJP%20Says%20Chief%20Minister%20Should%20Resign%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20protests%20over%20the%20rape-murder%20of%20a%20young%20doctor%20in%20Kolkata's%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20still%20churning%20the%20country%2C%20the%20BJP%20today%20dubbed%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20the%20%26quot%3Bdestroyer%26quot%3B%20and%20claimed%20that%20name%20has%20been%20changed%20by%20the%20people%20to%20%26quot%3BNirmamata%20Banerjee%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20this%20horrific%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20the%20media%2C%20BJP%20spokesperson%20Gaurav%20Bhatia%20demanded%20that%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20resign%20from%20the%20post%20of%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%C2%A0%26quot%3BMamata%20Banerjee%20has%20become%20Mamata%20the%20destroyer.%20By%20her%20misdeeds%20she%20has%20destroyed%20the%20dignity%20of%20a%20woman%2C%20a%20doctor%20who%20was%20serving%20the%20society%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20he%20added%2C%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bdestroyer%20of%20the%20rule%20of%20law%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20anarchist%20Mamata%20Banerjee.%20She%20is%20the%20destroyer%20of%20evidence%20in%20this%20heinous%20crime...%20(through%20her)%20acts%20of%20omission%20or%20commission.%20She%20is%20the%20destroyer%20of%20the%20constitution%20of%20our%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reason%2C%20he%20said%2C%20was%20that%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20is%20protecting%20the%20former%20principal%20of%20the%20medical%20college%20whose%20job%20it%20was%20to%20protect%20the%20students%20and%20in%20which%20he%20failed.%20%26quot%3BLet%20alone%20investigating%20him%2C%20she%20rewarded%20him%20and%20is%20standing%20with%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BShe%20also%20destroyed%20a%20woman's%20self-respect.%20She%20destroyed%20the%20constitutional%20values%20she%20had%20sworn%20to%20protect.%20She%20is%20destroying%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20and%20finally%2C%20the%20evidence%20in%20the%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%2C%20Bengal%20Governor%20CV%20Ananda%20Bose%20ripped%20into%20the%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20government%2C%20saying%20it%20has%20failed%20the%20women%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBengal%20is%20not%20a%20place%20safe%20for%20women.%20Bengal%20has%20failed%20its%20women.%20Not%20the%20society%20but%20the%20present%20government%20has%20failed%20its%20women%20folk...%20the%20government%20has%20ensured%20that%20a%20woman%20has%20no%20protection%2C%20which%20is%20what%20is%20reflected%20after%20the%20gruesome%20tragedy%20that%20took%20place%20in%20RG%20Kar.%20This%20should%20not%20be%20repeated%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Governor%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20also%20been%20criticised%20massively%20for%20its%20new%20notification%20listing%20rules%20for%20workplaces%20where%20women%20work%20at%20night.%20%C2%A0%20%26quot%3BWherever%20possible%2C%20night%20duty%20may%20be%20avoided%20for%20women.%20We%20hope%20these%20measures%20are%20implemented%20at%20the%20earliest%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Alapan%20Bandopadhyay%2C%20the%20Chief%20Advisor%20to%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Banerjee%20has%20accused%20the%20Left%20and%20the%20BJP%20of%20conspiring%20against%20her.%20%26quot%3BThey%20want%20to%20create%20unrest%20in%20Bengal%20and%20they%20both%20have%20come%20together%20to%20do%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20had