2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fterror-attack-in-pakistan-kills-three-security-personnel%2Famp_articleshow%2F112627131.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Engineer%20Friends%20Build%20AI-Enabled%20Hydroponic%20Set%20up%20to%20Grow%20Exotic%20Plants%3B%20Earn%20Rs%2050%20Lakh%2FYear%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESince%20time%20immemorial%2C%20farmers%20have%20relied%20on%20rain%2C%20soil%20fertility%2C%20and%20expensive%20pesticides%20to%20grow%20their%20crops.%20Often%2C%20they%20would%20end%20up%20in%20a%20debt%20trap%20after%20incurring%20huge%20crop%20losses%20owing%20to%20unseasonal%20rains%2C%20hailstorm%2C%20and%20decreasing%20soil%20fertility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20two%20college%20friends%20delved%20into%20this%20sector%20with%20a%20strong%20desire%20to%20revolutionise%20farming%20practices.%20Calvin%20Aranha%20and%20Farish%20Anfal%20have%20integrated%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20(AI)%20into%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F307986%2Fahmedabad-friends-offer-training-earn-crores-with-rise-hydroponics-startup%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehydroponic%20farms%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20grow%20crops!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20their%20vertical%20farm%20in%20Brahmavara%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20they%20are%20growing%20exotic%20crops%20such%20as%20lettuce%2C%20basil%2C%20kale%20and%20parsley%20using%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20after%20completing%20their%20engineering%20at%20the%20Mangalore%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20and%20Engineering%20(MITE)%20in%20Moodabidri%20that%20the%20Udupi-based%20friends%20aspired%20to%20work%20in%20the%20agriculture%20sector.%20Although%20Calvin%20went%20on%20to%20work%20in%20Bengaluru%20in%20the%20corporate%20world%2C%20Farish%20started%20a%20small%20seafood%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20his%20work%2C%20Farish%20says%20he%20learnt%20about%20the%20various%20issues%20faced%20by%20farmers%20at%20the%20grassroots%20level.%20%E2%80%9CI%20found%20that%20farmers%20were%20facing%20a%20lot%20of%20challenges%20in%20making%20farming%20profitable%20due%20to%20climate%20change.%20I%20talked%20to%20more%20farmers%20and%20came%20to%20know%20the%20gravity%20of%20problems%20faced%20by%20them%20on%20a%20regular%20basis%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FKrop-AI-2-1723817299.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Calvin%20and%20Farish%20aimed%20to%20boost%20farmers%E2%80%99%20income%20and%20resilience%20against%20climate%20fluctuations.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FKrop-AI-2-1723817299.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FKrop-AI-2-1723817299-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FKrop-AI-2-1723817299-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FKrop-AI-2-1723817299-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FKrop-AI-2-1723817299-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-361736%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ECalvin%20and%20Farish%20aimed%20to%20boost%20farmers%E2%80%99%20income%20and%20resilience%20against%20climate%20fluctuations.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarish%20continues%20to%20reiterate%20that%20Indian%20farmers%20are%20largely%20dependent%20on%20soil%2C%20water%2C%20and%20weather.%20%E2%80%9CWith%20rising%20input%20costs%20and%20poor%20yields%2C%20they%20incur%20huge%20losses%20and%20fall%20into%20subsequent%20debts.%20Hydroponics%20seemed%20a%20very%20good%20segment%20as%20it%20requires%2095%20percent%20less%20water%20and%20crops%20can%20be%20grown%20in%20a%20controlled%20environment%20with%20artificial%20light%20without%20depending%20on%20the%20weather%20outside%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Calvin%20points%20out%20that%20while%20groundwater%20is%20already%20depleting%20to%20severe%20levels%20and%20agricultural%20lands%20are%20decreasing%2C%20demand%20for%20food%20continues%20to%20increase.%20%E2%80%9CClimate%20change%20is%20rapid%20and%20crop%20loss%20will%20be%20substantial%20due%20to%20this.%20We%20understood%20that%20innovation%20in%20a%20controlled%20environment%20is%20crucial%20and%20AI%20will%20help%20us%20further%20our%20sustainable%20goals%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20weekend%2C%20Calvin%20and%20Farish%20spoke%20in%20detail%20on%20the%20persistent%20issue.%20With%20a%20shared%20passion%20for%20transforming%20the%20agricultural%20sector%20through%20technology-driven%20solutions%2C%20they%20eventually%20decided%20to%20completely%20shift%20their%20focus%20on%20making%20farming%20profitable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Calvin%20quit%20his%20job%20and%20both%20friends%20rented%20a%20small%20flat%20in%20Udupi%20where%20they%20built%20a%20prototype%20using%20their%20pocket%20money.%20After%20four%20months%2C%20they%20started%20their%20company%2C%20Krop%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECutting%20operational%20costs%20to%20half%20with%20AI%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20offering%20container%20farm%20setups%20as%20an%20alternative%20to%20traditional%20polyhouse%20farming%2C%20Calvin%20and%20Farish%20aimed%20to%20boost%20farmers%E2%80%99%20income%20and%20resilience%20against%20climate%20fluctuations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebet