20wavelengths%20required%20for%20plant%20growth.%20An%20ideal%20plant%20requires%20light%20wavelengths%20between%20600%20and%20700%20nanometers%20for%20photosynthesis.%20For%20human%20eyes%2C%20they%20look%20purplish%20blue%20in%20colour%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Calvin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECompared%20to%20traditional%20farming%20methods%2C%20the%20AI-enabled%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F356971%2Fhydroponics-farming-without-soil-sustainable-agriculture-farmer-increases-income-solar-energy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehydroponic%20farming%20%3C%2Fa%3Emethod%20not%20only%20saves%2095%20percent%20of%20water%20as%20it%20is%20reused%20in%20the%20setup%20but%20also%20brings%20operational%20costs%20to%2050%20percent.%20This%2C%20Farish%20says%2C%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20make%20agriculture%20more%20sustainable%20and%20profitable%20for%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FKrop-AI-3-1723817396.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20system%20maintains%20parametres%20like%20temperature%2C%20humidity%2C%20pH%2C%20to%20provide%20an%20ideal%20environment%20suitable%20for%20plant%20growth.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FKrop-AI-3-1723817396.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FKrop-AI-3-1723817396-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FKrop-AI-3-1723817396-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FKrop-AI-3-1723817396-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FKrop-AI-3-1723817396-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-361738%5C%