-farming-technique%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThis%2520method%2520of%2520farming%2520%25E2%2580%2594%2520hydroponics%2Cstart%252C%2520we%2520have%2520you%2520covered.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewithout%20sun%20and%20soil%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20without%20compromising%20the%20taste.%20We%20are%20glad%20that%20within%20two%20years%20of%20time%2C%20we%20have%20not%20only%20been%20able%20to%20work%20on%20our%20patented%20technology%20but%20also%20revolutionised%20farming%20solutions%20for%20farmers.%20We%20hope%20to%20scale%20up%20the%20work%20and%20reach%20to%20small%20and%20medium%20income%20growers%20so%20that%20they%20can%20benefit%20from%20our%20technology%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Farish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%20All%20photos%3A%20Calvin%20Aranha.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724062679000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FKrop-AI-2-1723817299.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D361688%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Calvin%20Aranha%20and%20Farish%20Anfal%2C%20from%20Udupi%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20started%20Krop%20AI.%20The%20hydroponics%20startup%20integrates%20technology%20and%20automation%20to%20enhance%20crop%20quality%20and%20production.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F361688%2Fartificial-intelligence-ai-hydroponic-farming-grow-exotic-vegetables-farms-climate-change-krop-ai-udupi-startup%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kamala%20Harris'%20nomination%20ignites%20local%20organizers%20to%20rally%20Black%20voters%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724062255000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112627401%2Cimgsize-699013.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fkamala-harris-nomination-ignites-local-organizers-to-