%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F332716%2Fjanaki-amma-swimming-lessons-for-women-kids-reduce-drowning-deaths-in-kerala%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereturned%20to%20the%20pool%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%202022%2C%20as%20if%20it%20were%20yesterday.%20Swimming%20after%2018%20years%20was%20one%20of%20her%20happiest%20moments%2C%20she%20recalls.%20It%20was%20the%20day%20she%20felt%20whole%20again%2C%20having%20rediscovered%20the%20missing%20piece%20of%20her%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20muscle%20memory%20kicked%20in%20and%20as%20I%20went%20underwater%2C%20I%20realised%20that%20this%20was%20what%20I%20wanted.%20This%20was%20my%20happy%20place.%20I%20cried%20that%20day%20as%20it%20gave%20me%20so%20much%20joy%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tanvi%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETanvi%20began%20her%20training%20for%20the%20English%20Channel%20swim%20under%20the%20guidance%20of%20coach%20Srikaanth%20Viswanathan%2C%20an%20accomplished%20open-water%20swimmer%20who%20had%20completed%20the%20triple%20crown%20of%20open-water%20swimming.%20Her%20practice%20sessions%20started%20at%204%20am%2C%20requiring%20her%20to%20wake%20up%20at%203%20am.%20The%20sudden%20shift%20in%20routine%20was%20challenging%2C%20especially%20with%20three-year-old%20twins.%20It%20was%20a%20rollercoaster%20ride%2C%20she%20admits%2C%20involving%20a%20complete%20overhaul%20of%20her%20lifestyle%20and%20schedule.%20Her%20children%20were%20too%20young%20to%20grasp%20the%20magnitude%20of%20what%20their%20mother%20was%20attempting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201071px)%20100vw%2C%201071px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftanvi-with-dad-min-1723815119.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221071%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tanvi%20with%20her%20biggest%20cheerleader%2C%20her%20father.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fupl