%20traces%20back%20to%20the%20Harappan%20Civilisation%20(3300-1300%20BC)%3F%20A%202024%20research%20study%20published%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EInternational%20Journal%20of%20Novel%20Research%20and%20Development%3C%2Fem%3E%20highlighted%20the%20eco-benefits%20of%20terracotta%20pointing%20to%20its%20energy%20efficiency.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20firing%20process%20used%20in%20terracotta%20production%20typically%20requires%20lower%20temperatures%20compared%20to%20other%20ceramics%20and%20building%20materials%20like%20concrete%20or%20metals.%20It%20has%20reduced%20greenhouse%20gas%20emissions%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20paper%20noted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fsustainable-architecture-4-1723551751.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20terracotta%20tiles%20make%20for%20a%20beautiful%20design%20against%20the%20landscape%2C%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fsustainable-architecture-4-1723551751.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fsustainable-architecture-4-1723551751-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fsustainable-architecture-4-1723551751-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fsustainable-architecture-4-1723551751-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fsustainable-architecture-4-1723551751-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-361167%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20terracotta%20tiles%20make%20for%20a%20beautiful%20design%20against%20the%20landscape%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20GPM%20Architects%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2