tely%20decided%20to%20quit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20first%20moved%20to%20Mumbai%20for%20work%2C%20it%20took%20me%20two%20months%20to%20find%20a%20hostel%20with%20a%20lift%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%20It%20was%20during%20this%20period%20that%20she%20became%20resolute%20in%20her%20goal%20to%20bring%20attention%20to%20the%20challenges%20faced%20by%20people%20like%20herself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EUsing%20her%20voice%20to%20push%20for%20greater%20accessibility%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESweta%20shares%20that%20her%20parents%20have%20always%20motivated%20her%20to%20use%20her%20voice%20for%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20trip%20to%20Rajasthan%20in%202007%2C%20she%20was%20amazed%20to%20find%20Western-style%20toilets%20even%20at%20small%20highway%20%3Cem%3Edhabas%3C%2Fem%3E.%20When%20she%20asked%20why%2C%20the%20owners%20said%20it%20was%20for%20expats.%20She%20wondered%3A%20if%20the%20Government%20can%20be%20so%20accommodating%20to%20expats%2C%20why%20can%E2%80%99t%20they%20do%20the%20same%20for%20people%20with%20disabilities%3F%20As%20a%2020-year-old%2C%20she%20was%20infuriated.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20parents%20encouraged%20me%20to%20write%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20or%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls%20with%20a%20smile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20her%20earliest%20initiatives%20was%20a%20project%20called%20%E2%80%98Give%20Some%20Space%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20she%20launched%20with%20her%20friend%20Vishal%20Sawvaant%2C%20a%20wheelchair%20user.%20Together%2C%20they%20installed%20ramps%20on%20SB%20Road%2C%20Fergusson%20College%20Road%2C%20and%20nearby%20areas%20in%20Pune%2C%20making%20it%20easier%20for%20wheelchair%20users%20to%20access%20bookstores%2C%20restaurants%2C%20and%20educational%20institutions.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20lived%20reality%20of%20wheelchair%20users%20is%20so%20ignored%20that%20they%20often%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20have%20the%20option%20to%20visit%20a%20college%20to%20inquire%20about%20admission%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20points%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20Sweta%20and%20her%20cousin%20Nalini%20Mangwani%20created%20an%20art%20installation%20called%20the%20Restroom%20Project.%20The%20artwork%20depicted%20a%20map%20of%20restaurants%20in%20Pune%20on%20a%20cardboard%20canvas%20painted%20with%20bright%20blue%20strokes.%20The%20map%20included%20landmarks%20shaped%20like%20toilet%20seats%20to%20illustrate%20the%20challenges%20of%20finding%20disability-friendly%20restrooms.%20Opening%20each%20commode%20lid%20on%20the%20canvas%20revealed%20whether%20the%20restaurant%20was%20accessible%20by%20people%20with%20disabilities%2C%20whether%20there%20were%20steps%20to%20the%20restroom%20or%20other%20relevant%20features.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20how%20she%20sees%20her%20comedy%20progressing%2C%20Sweta%20says%20that%20there%20are%20many%20aspects%20of%20her%20life%20that%20she%E2%80%99s%20yet%20to%20figure%20out%2C%20including%20nuances%20of%20living%20with%20a%20disability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20definitely%20want%20to%20talk%20more%20about%20the%20role%20that%20upbringing%20and%20conditioning%20play%20in%20the%20context%20of%20people%E2%80%99s%20perception%20of%20people%20with%20disabilities.%20Sometimes%2C%20even%20after%20seeing%20me%20on%20stage%2C%20people%20still%20believe%20that%20those%20with%20disabilities%20should%20stay%20quiet%20and%20not%20talk%20about%20their%20challenges%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20message%20to%20people%20with%20disabilities%20thinking%20about%20getting%20into%20stand-up%20comedy%20is%20simple%3A%20%E2%80%9COwn%20your%20space%20and%20speak%20boldly.%20Speak%20your%20mind%20confidently%2C%20without%20worrying%20about%20how%20others%20might%20react.%20Be%20yourself%20and%20don%E2%80%99t%20change%20who%20you%20are%20to%20fit%20into%20a%20mould.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EYou%20can%20book%20Sweta%20for%20shows%20by%20contacting%20her%20via%20Instagram%20(%40imadmantrii)%2C%20LinkedIn%2C%20or%20email%20at%20iamadmantrii%40gmail.com.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Images%20Courtesy%20Sweta%20Mantrii)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723473351000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-21_11zon-1723470978.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D360927%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Once%20unsure%20if%20she%20could%20even%20climb%20up%20the%20stage%2C%20Sweta%20Mantrii%20has%20now%20completed%20over%20300%20comedy%20shows%20and%20is%20committed%20to%20making%20public%20spaces%20more%20inclusive%20for%20people%20with%20disabilities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tanvi%20Dalvi%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F360927%2Fsweta-mantrii-comedian-spina-bifida-disability-stand-up-comedy-wheelchair-accessibility-inclusion%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2230%20Years%2C%20101%20Elephant%20Corridors%3A%20Vivek%20Menon%E2%80%99s%20Blueprint%20for%20Elephant%20Protection%20in%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20couple%20of%20decades%20ago%2C%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20Uttarakhand%E2%80%99s%20Jim%20Corbett%20National%20Park%2C%20a%20youth%20could%20be%20seen%20hiding%20high%20up%20in%20one%20of%20the%20watch%20towers.%20Anyone%20passing%20by%20would%20wonder%20about%20the%20unusual%20spot%20he%20had%20picked.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20answer%20lay%20in%20an%20amusing%20scene%3B%20every%20time%20the%20young%20boy%20attempted%20to%20make%20his%20way%20out%20of%20the%20tower%2C%20an%20elephant%20(camouflaged%20by%20the%20thicket%20of%20bushes)%20would%20appear%20and%20charge%20at%20him.%20And%20once%20again%2C%20the%20boy%20would%20ascend%20the%20watch%20tower%20and%20wait.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20all%20of%20four%20hours%20before%20the%20elephant%20decided%20to%20make%20a%20move%20and%20the%20youth%20finally%20descended%20the%20watch%20tower%2C%20relief%20colouring%20his%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20boy%20in%20this%20story%20was%20a%20young%20Vivek%20Menon%2C%20who%20is%20now%20the%20co-founder%20of%20Wildlife%20Trust%20of%20India%20%E2%80%94%20an%20organisation%20dedicated%20to%20the%20preservation%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F236243%2Fganesh-chaturthi-wild-elephant-protection-love-heroes-conservation-protection-mahout-assam-tamil-nadu-india-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprotection%20of%20wild%20habitats%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20tryst%20with%20the%20elephant%20left%20an%20indelible%20mark%20on%20Menon%E2%80%99s%20mind.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20made%20me%20understand%20the%20animal%E2%80%99s%20strength%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles%2C%20quick%20to%20add%2C%20however%2C%20that%20his%20love%20for%20the%20wild%20and%20nature%20predates%20this%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20singular%20story%20that%20served%20as%20inspiration%20to%20become%20a%20conservationist%2C%20Menon%20insists.%20But%20coax%20him%20a%20little%2C%20and%20he%20says%20genetics%20did%20play%20its%20role%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20from%20Kerala%2C%20the%20land%20of%20elephants%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%20as%20did%20childhood%20treks.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20were%20treks%20to%20the%20Himalayas%20during%20my%20school%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20Menon%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20would%20be%20right%20to%20say%20that%20I%20took%20to%20animals%20and%20birds%20the%20moment%20I%20was%20exposed%20to%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20home%2C%20Menon%E2%80%99s%20room%20resembled%20an%20animal%20shelter.%20Birds%20and%20small%20animals%20rescued%20from%20the%20wild%20and%20predatory%20hands%20found%20a%20safe%20space.%20%E2%80%9CI%20thought%20I%20was%20doing%20them%20%5Bthe%20animals%5D%20good%20by%20bringing%20them%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20justifies.%20Today%2C%20at%2056%2C%20the%20conservationist%E2%80%99s%20w